(2159,	NULL,	NULL,	'Que tome un curso en la UNAB electivo o extensión, que tenga las mismas competencias que el curso de los pilares de competencias digitales.
Que tenga una insignia validada por entidad tales como certik, acredita, Credly, que indique aprobado, y tenga las competencias definidas relacionadas con los cursos del pilar a aplicar.
La propuesta también contempla un Plan de Virtualización que garantizará la disponibilidad progresiva de los cursos para estudiantes de programas virtuales y permitirá su uso flexible en otras modalidades. Esta virtualización se extenderá entre los periodos 202560 y 202620, asegurando que para el 202710 los cursos estén plenamente implementados en modalidad virtual.
Finalmente, se establece que la oferta podrá ser dinámica y evolutiva, permitiendo incluir o actualizar cursos en función de las innovaciones tecnológicas y las necesidades particulares de los programas académicos, lo que garantiza la vigencia, pertinencia y adaptabilidad del modelo.',	'[-0.025405884,0.048034668,0.047729492,0.006919861,-0.01058197,0.0069465637,0.005054474,0.030166626,0.009773254,0.029159546,0.05328369,-0.019943237,-0.016433716,-0.05038452,-0.0072898865,0.05130005,0.004085541,-0.019058228,0.011001587,0.042510986,0.015151978,-0.036071777,-0.016220093,0.035888672,0.01386261,-0.022399902,0.03543091,0.050842285,-0.026062012,-0.015960693,0.02708435,-0.03463745,-0.032318115,-0.012802124,0.00093746185,0.03353882,-0.027236938,0.049316406,-0.003396988,-0.022521973,-0.0059814453,0.008621216,0.0028839111,0.00056505203,-0.050048828,0.024475098,-0.015357971,-0.024154663,-0.0009918213,0.048919678,-0.02734375,0.0061187744,0.038024902,0.033294678,-0.033996582,-0.010505676,0.013870239,-0.006603241,-0.0042762756,-0.017593384,0.025756836,0.03665161,0.030670166,0.049194336,0.02355957,0.019332886,-0.038757324,0.044952393,-0.04119873,-0.009109497,-0.018981934,0.007408142,0.008041382,-0.014984131,-0.010345459,0.052490234,0.037353516,0.02456665,0.002298355,-0.022720337,-0.03692627,0.022460938,0.03982544,-0.041229248,-0.014854431,0.0044059753,-0.057647705,-0.02130127,-0.010383606,-0.0076904297,-0.01612854,0.029571533,-0.051086426,0.034973145,0.011985779,0.049987793,0.03677368,-0.04586792,0.0107803345,0.020095825,0.009796143,-0.047943115,0.011962891,-0.018661499,0.024673462,-0.027877808,0.03050232,0.022094727,-0.03778076,0.015640259,0.029327393,0.009773254,0.034698486,-0.0024089813,0.027938843,-0.081726074,-0.01828003,-0.046966553,-0.009422302,-0.0033798218,-0.02923584,-0.022872925,-0.029418945,-0.03012085,-0.013618469,-0.06536865,0.019607544,-0.0018510818,-0.032409668,-0.03213501,-0.054504395,0.0035362244,0.011878967,0.0032024384,-0.009376526,0.008682251,-0.04623413,-0.01875