(2161,	NULL,	NULL,	'En la actualidad, las instituciones de educación superior enfrentan un entorno en constante transformación, donde la tecnología redefine el modo en que se aprende, se trabaja y se interactúa socialmente. Informes globales como el Futuro del Empleo 2025 del Foro Económico Mundial, y marcos de referencia como DigComp 2.2 de la Unión Europea, las Competencias Digitales de la UNESCO y la propuesta de la OEA sobre alfabetización digital para América Latina, coinciden en la necesidad urgente de que las universidades reformulen sus currículos para incluir habilidades digitales transversales.',	'[-0.00038218498,0.0052604675,0.045318604,0.014923096,0.04159546,0.027313232,0.038208008,0.06951904,-0.015640259,0.007499695,-0.014038086,-0.027908325,-0.029830933,-0.020080566,-0.0011081696,0.013458252,-0.006389618,-0.03866577,0.030578613,0.026107788,0.010040283,-0.047729492,-0.0034008026,0.015129089,0.015930176,-0.01965332,0.00096178055,0.051086426,-0.064819336,0.032409668,0.008293152,-0.037841797,-0.042419434,-0.016342163,0.03302002,0.031555176,-0.044647217,0.058502197,0.011428833,-0.0070381165,0.010871887,0.019821167,-0.00541687,-0.019485474,-0.03475952,-0.022521973,-0.027114868,-0.047729492,0.03164673,0.060180664,-0.03302002,-0.011291504,0.04751587,0.039276123,-0.018310547,0.0061683655,-0.011978149,-0.007499695,-0.027420044,0.020568848,0.049346924,0.035003662,0.043273926,0.023544312,-0.026550293,0.015151978,-0.024230957,0.0074920654,-0.05633545,-0.015563965,0.019210815,-0.005142212,0.00091552734,0.010925293,-0.025802612,0.0158844,0.011329651,-0.0045661926,-0.019485474,0.010620117,-0.0065994263,-0.008758545,0.0021305084,-0.013244629,0.0030822754,0.07104492,-0.0141067505,-0.04220581,-0.031677246,-0.012313843,-0.040527344,-0.0049591064,-0.042663574,0.035339355,-0.041931152,0.015602112,0.0020599365,-0.016052246,0.004047394,0.059509277,-0.010505676,-0.018203735,0.025100708,-0.008880615,-0.014541626,-0.009254456,-0.019378662,-0.032165527,-0.0368042,-0.015365601,-0.