(2163,	NULL,	NULL,	'Figura 1.
A esta perspectiva global se suma con especial relevancia el diagnóstico regional presentado en estudios como "Tech Skills for Latin America and the Caribbean". Estas iniciativas, a menudo fruto de alianzas entre el sector tecnológico y organismos multilaterales, van un paso más allá de los marcos de competencias generales. Su objetivo es identificar la brecha específica entre las habilidades digitales que poseen los egresados y las que demanda activamente el mercado laboral de la región, subrayando que para impulsar la transformación productiva y mejorar la empleabilidad, es crucial enfocarse en competencias técnicas que están redefiniendo las industrias locales.',	'[0.015640259,0.020095825,0.06488037,0.015571594,0.005115509,0.019470215,0.03567505,0.078430176,0.008216858,-0.017211914,-0.013427734,0.02520752,-0.030960083,-0.04598999,-0.008720398,0.03982544,-0.045532227,-0.060272217,0.038208008,0.011070251,0.037475586,-0.036621094,-0.0067977905,0.0063056946,0.012924194,0.008171082,-0.023590088,0.058563232,-0.029830933,0.018798828,0.0018663406,-0.035491943,-0.029022217,-0.025390625,0.051361084,0.02444458,-0.017089844,0.07946777,0.03967285,-0.01146698,0.02305603,0.019348145,-0.043395996,0.006187439,-0.034210205,-0.06738281,-0.031921387,-0.03250122,0.032318115,0.038208008,-0.025741577,0.0025234222,0.022399902,0.0069770813,-0.029037476,-0.015838623,-0.001033783,0.009384155,0.016525269,0.00819397,0.06488037,-0.0051612854,0.06707764,0.04989624,-0.01890564,0.024291992,-0.019882202,-0.014717102,-0.04232788,-0.024276733,0.028137207,0.015571594,0.01360321,0.021606445,-0.008041382,0.0063934326,-0.0059814453,0.037994385,-0.01335144,0.019638062,-0.005973816,-0.016174316,0.04623413,-0.039642334,-0.0045547485,0.022949219,-0.007419586,-0.05770874,-0.049957275,0.022338867,-0.051727295,0.0068206787,0.0076675415,0.022399902,-0.033569336,0.03262329,-0.006668091,-0.021896362,0.006038666,0.042236328,0.021881104,0.035461426,0.023513794,-0.049194336,0.0012788773,0.006526947,-0.025650024,0.0