(2164,	NULL,	NULL,	'Este enfoque pragmático refuerza la necesidad de que la oferta formativa, no solo desarrolle una ciudadanía digital crítica, sino que también proporcione una base sólida para el futuro. Habilidades en áreas como el análisis de datos, la gestión de la nube (cloud computing), la ciberseguridad y la comprensión práctica de la inteligencia artificial ya no son un nicho, sino un requisito para la competitividad profesional en América Latina. Por tanto, alinear el pilar de " Analítica y contenido digital "  y “”Tecnologías Transformativas”  con estas demandas regionales asegura que la formación inicial de los estudiantes sea pertinente, actual y un verdadero catalizador para su desarrollo profesional futuro.
Tomado de:  LATAM learners will prioritise AI in 2025',	'[0.00016224384,0.035339355,0.028396606,0.0010795593,0.066833496,-0.026733398,0.032073975,0.1038208,-0.01411438,0.018829346,0.012145996,0.002029419,0.00070238113,-0.052703857,-0.009208679,0.012779236,-0.017486572,-0.040924072,0.059020996,0.006095886,0.030792236,-0.037353516,-0.031555176,0.0019893646,-0.007335663,-0.021240234,0.027572632,0.043640137,-0.08520508,0.011459351,0.0413208,-0.030059814,-0.038970947,0.0010719299,0.032562256,0.015014648,-0.023452759,0.054138184,0.023651123,-0.004432678,0.009300232,-0.006362915,-0.011375427,0.011962891,-0.029556274,-0.022720337,0.0046844482,-0.0473938,0.0070877075,0.047180176,-0.0491333,-0.013664246,0.034179688,0.03692627,-0.029922485,0.0013961792,-0.017150879,0.0061683655,0.008285522,0.013198853,0.057556152,-0.0044403076,0.028121948,0.033996582,0.0007863045,0.010261536,-0.02420044,-0.015670776,-0.038879395,-0.02444458,0.0096588135,-0.012199402,0.029037476,0.00869751,-0.046081543,0.026565552,-0.027938843,0.023834229,-0.024627686,0.0096206665,-0.019744873,0.015655518,0.05645752,-0.050598145,-0.018844604,0.00045371056,-0.059020996,-0.024871826,-0.024734497,0.0030822754,-0.01651001,-0.02230835,-0.03930664,0.0463562,-0.010902405,0.053588867,0.01020813,-0.013725281,0.016662598,0.0491333,0.002714157,-0.03201294,0.012184143,0.00111866,-0.0033435822,-0.016998291,0.021362305,-0.0046081543,-0.016525269,-0.005844116,-0.011550903,-0.020141602,-0.0070343018,0.017913818,0.017608643,-0.064331055,-0.011413574,-0.0262146,0.010612488,0.034729004,0.006149292,-0.02696228,-0.03967285,0.010566711,-0.058898926,-0.0692749,0.035064697,-0.020935059,-0.026153564,-0.05505371,-0.05001831,0.0067367554,0.012199402,-0.019454956,-0.0044898987,-0.011711121,-0.030853271,-0.029632568,-0.015159607,-0.04888916,0.034698486,0.0008635521,-0.0026378632,0.026412964,-0.040924072,-0.043273926,0.000121593475,0.042999268,0.027862549,0.08288574,-0.023162842,-0.027999878,-0.061950684,0.00655365,0.024871826,-0.023544312,