(2165,	NULL,	NULL,	'En este contexto, la Universidad Autónoma de Bucaramanga (UNAB) ha decidido actualizar el Componente Instrumental; el cual, si bien no forma parte formal del plan de estudios de los programas de pregrado profesional, sí constituye un requisito de formación transversal obligatorio. Esta decisión responde a múltiples factores: por un lado, las necesidades actuales de los estudiantes de pregrado, quienes requieren una formación digital alineada con los cambios tecnológicos, y por otro, las exigencias del sector productivo, que demandan competencias digitales prácticas en todos los campos del saber. En programas técnicos y tecnológicos (T&T), así como en los de modalidad dual, este componente tiene un papel aún más central, ya que se integra dentro de los cursos formales que ya tienen dentro del plan de estudios, siendo clave para el desarrollo de capacidades técnicas aplicadas desde etapas tempranas. Esta actualización permite a la UNAB no solo formar ciudadanos íntegros y éticos,',	'[-0.02645874,0.02734375,0.0077819824,0.021194458,0.0064201355,0.012214661,0.0262146,0.048675537,-0.030136108,-0.015357971,0.0010719299,-0.0062561035,-0.011482239,-0.026977539,0.038391113,0.022003174,0.0032672882,-0.017501831,-0.0026111603,-0.005958557,0.019500732,-0.051239014,0.011421204,0.007423401,0.000579834,-0.028945923,0.005683899,0.06756592,-0.03817749,-0.016799927,0.0055160522,-0.042938232,-0.031463623,-0.008232117,-0.013961792,0.015991211,-0.019897461,0.030349731,0.003704071,-0.011116028,0.00945282,0.019561768,-0.03540039,-0.012550354,-0.031402588,0.010955811,-0.02619934,-0.02418518,-0.011657715,0.025054932,-0.04724121,-0.01360321,0.048797607,0.015640259,-0.022140503,0.024017334,-0.040496826,0.0008583069,0.0026931763,-0.014450073,0.03164673,0.026535034,0.016525269,0.04663086,-0.017562866,-0.018676758,-0.020233154,0.021591187,-0.036834717,-0.029434204,0.020080566,-0.0018320084,-0.010406494,0.037506104,-0.03729248,0.0748291,0.004108429,0.030059814,-0.01939392,0.01