(2166,	NULL,	NULL,	'los cursos formales que ya tienen dentro del plan de estudios, siendo clave para el desarrollo de capacidades técnicas aplicadas desde etapas tempranas. Esta actualización permite a la UNAB no solo formar ciudadanos íntegros y éticos, preparados para la vida y el trabajo en un mundo digitalizado, sino también garantizar la pertinencia de su oferta educativa frente a los retos de la empleabilidad, la productividad y la transformación digital del entorno regional y nacional.',	'[0.011627197,0.042816162,0.025039673,0.006717682,-0.0037994385,-0.0049552917,0.048461914,0.075683594,0.0031261444,0.013282776,0.030090332,0.011741638,-0.019760132,-0.028015137,0.0043258667,0.039215088,-0.020996094,-0.030349731,0.00945282,0.014190674,0.029464722,-0.056030273,-0.010612488,-0.021530151,-0.017562866,-0.021316528,0.016357422,0.03656006,-0.053131104,-0.000259161,-0.0045318604,-0.033233643,-0.0362854,-0.00856781,-0.004131317,0.029220581,-0.0051460266,0.04660034,0.0071907043,-0.012168884,0.00881958,0.0046958923,0.00082731247,-0.033203125,-0.05239868,0.0030460358,-0.023025513,-0.0014734268,-0.002538681,0.029953003,-0.048309326,0.020812988,0.047088623,0.01663208,-0.02017212,0.0016794205,-0.0121154785,-0.028015137,-0.0038661957,-0.030715942,0.039093018,0.032470703,0.045654297,0.05911255,-0.019485474,-0.0043525696,-0.03591919,0.022018433,-0.030380249,-0.02607727,0.019821167,-0.046417236,-0.0093307495,-0.0030231476,-0.024215698,0.04196167,0.026565552,0.030075073,-0.011299133,0.020599365,-0.00082731247,0.014923096,0.027572632,-0.033111572,-0.030380249,0.017211914,-0.06124878,-0.047454834,-0.026733398,0.00056886673,-0.017974854,0.027053833,-0.02947998,0.04220581,-0.011528015,0.049041748,0.023727417,-0.041412354,0.035827637,0.008834839,0.031555176,-0.019592285,0.009498596,-0.055877686,-0.012237549,-0.025817871,-0.033050537,-0.042266846,-0.048919678,0.012481689,-0.0020198822,-0.03488159,0.013618469,-0.012397766,0.04525757,-0.079833984,-0.02508545,-0.032318115,-0.008155823,0.