(2168,	NULL,	NULL,	'La UNAB ha venido avanzando en la alineación de sus cursos con estándares internacionales, en particular mediante la transformación del componente de Informática Básica hacia un modelo de Cultura Informática, basado en las certificaciones IC3 (Internet Core Competency Certification) y MOS (Microsoft Office Specialist).
Los cinco cursos actualmente ofrecidos bajo este modelo son:
Cultura Digital y MS PowerPoint (antes Introducción a los Computadores)
Vida en Línea (antes Internet Básico)
MS Word (antes Procesador de Texto Básico)
MS Excel (antes Hoja Electrónica Básica)
Cada curso puede ser cursado de manera presencial o virtual en ciclos de cuatro semanas, distribuidos a lo largo del semestre. La estructura académica incluye procesos definidos de inscripción, pago, bajas y calificación. Estos cursos, sin embargo, continúan enfocándose principalmente en herramientas tradicionales (Word, Excel, PowerPoint) sin incorporar competencias emergentes que demanda el mundo actual.',	'[-0.04107666,0.02659607,0.07922363,0.013748169,-0.033325195,-0.0105896,0.021347046,0.074035645,-0.006576538,0.051513672,0.010513306,-0.029083252,-0.026260376,-0.0020561218,-0.0051841736,0.049957275,-0.030349731,-0.017715454,-0.013038635,0.0234375,0.042297363,-0.030212402,0.01210022,0.038146973,-0.014755249,-0.00044727325,0.0009331703,0.07141113,-0.0015773773,-0.03970337,0.02255249,-0.036376953,0.0047073364,0.01940918,-0.012641907,0.028396606,-0.02217102,0.058563232,0.042999268,-0.021743774,0.0044555664,0.020904541,0.024398804,-0.0042266846,-0.02178955,0.016235352,-0.008888245,-0.019592285,0.031311035,0.040740967,-0.05532837,0.0036087036,0.042938232,0.035614014,-0.02079773,-0.01878357,0.009841919,-0.0027675629,-0.0037937164,-0.046173096,0.032806396,0.0005559921,0.032989502,0.036376953,-0.004878998,0.0009531975,-0.035095215,0.008544922,-0.034729004,-0.026565552,-0.026779175,0.0012454987,-0.02456665,-0.003528595,-0.03933716,0.08459473,0.0013570786,0.03060913,-0.01184845,-0.00086927414,0.018341064,-0.0032539368,0.04171753,-0.041992188,0.0040397644,0.031082153,-0.050476074,-0.003452301,-0.033477783,0.013755798,-0.035858154,0.011802673,-0.042938232,0.033233643,0.02923584,0.018585205,-0.00064468384,-0.016845703,0.021362305,0.024276733,0.008598328,-0.04260254,0.01713562,-0.037384033,0.027893066,-0.036346436,0.016983032,-0.038909912,-0.027236938,0.023666382,0.010429382,-0.007205963,0.03817749,-0.005455017,0.04034424,-0.03253174,0.017288208,-0.06750488,-0.011756897,-0.014595032,-0.041503906,-0.0011091232,-0.024169922,-0.039398193,-0.032684326,-0.016601562,0.029418945,0.0