(2170,	NULL,	NULL,	'En las reflexiones del grupo PEI sobre la competencia digital, demuestran que el modelo actual no de cohesión institucional presenta limitaciones pedagógicas y tecnológicas, y por lo tanto no responde adecuadamente ni a las expectativas de los estudiantes ni a las tendencias globales en educación digital.
En coherencia con ese trabajo de análisis, la Universidad Autónoma de Bucaramanga (UNAB) ha iniciado una reflexión profunda sobre el papel del componente instrumental —actualmente ofertado como Informática—. La actualización hacia una Ruta de Competencias Digitales responde no solo al diagnóstico institucional, sino también a las necesidades emergentes de estos programas, en los que se requiere una formación más contextualizada, alineada con las exigencias del sector productivo, el ritmo acelerado de transformación tecnológica y los perfiles de egreso orientados a la empleabilidad inmediata.',	'[0.0052871704,-0.00087594986,0.024490356,0.0121154785,0.033813477,0.008506775,0.040496826,0.07446289,-0.0075645447,0.0024204254,0.0008573532,-0.05001831,-0.0071372986,-0.050476074,-0.0044555664,0.015197754,0.009490967,-0.02607727,0.025497437,0.0597229,0.041931152,-0.051696777,0.0087509155,0.015174866,-0.004211426,-0.023620605,0.008163452,0.066589355,-0.050872803,-0.01272583,0.021820068,-0.026687622,-0.014564514,-0.045776367,-0.0044898987,0.050842285,-0.037628174,0.0647583,0.009246826,-5.8948994e-05,0.014541626,0.03869629,-0.04046631,-0.005908966,-0.05117798,-0.014122009,0.0058517456,-0.0115737915,0.021347046,0.010848999,-0.04748535,0.03466797,0.0791626,0.027236938,0.003168106,0.013633728,-0.0236969,-0.022140503,-0.012062073,0.01335144,0.034423828,0.0015468597,0.016937256,0.023590088,0.0027103424,0.00031208992,-0.025344849,0.02166748,-0.046722412,-0.035705566,0.02520752,0.0119018555,-0.0236969,0.031280518,-0.021957397,0.023422241,0.040802002,-0.0051498413,0.0057754517,0.016494751,-0.01889038,-0.0002450943,0.06738281,-0.02734375,-0.025543213,0.016189575,-0.04260254,-0.05581665,-0.024658203,-0.004070282,-0.025024414,0.021987915,-0.014442444,0.017211914,-0.006374359,0.0014038086,0.012954712,-0.02267456,0.040740967,0.04586792,0.005329132,-0.029144287,-0.002111435,-0.042022705,0.015716553,-0.010292053,-0.008293152,0.009178162,-0.041381836,-0.0079956055,0.0231781,-0.0039138794,0.000