(2171,	NULL,	NULL,	'Este proceso de cambio se enmarca en una visión institucional más amplia, la cual reconoce que la era digital —post-PC, marcada por tecnologías como la computación en la nube, big data, inteligencia artificial e internet de las cosas— plantea desafíos prioritarios para el currículo universitario. En este sentido, las preguntas clave que orientan el rediseño son: ¿Qué características requiere el currículo?, ¿Qué rol debe asumir el profesor?, y ¿Qué rol debe asumir el estudiante en esta nueva era? En espacios como los liderados por el equipo PEI, esta discusión ha resaltado la necesidad de articular el fundamento tecnológico con otros fundamentos esenciales —antropológico, psicológico, científico y pedagógico— para asegurar una formación humana integral. Así, el uso de la tecnología no se concibe como un fin en sí mismo, sino como un medio que potencia los propósitos del ser, hacer y conocer, en armonía con el modelo pedagógico institucional.',	'[0.008239746,-0.0031852722,0.034118652,0.016296387,0.054992676,-0.008110046,0.028900146,0.062683105,-0.037628174,0.009338379,0.04345703,-0.008705139,-0.024673462,-0.013442993,-0.009300232,0.021881104,-0.005947113,0.005783081,0.039733887,0.0317688,0.022903442,-0.024810791,0.0043640137,0.026672363,0.009002686,-0.030639648,0.026626587,0.046569824,-0.025985718,0.022384644,0.007835388,-0.021743774,-0.05230713,-0.018341064,0.008384705,0.0072784424,-0.06665039,0.045959473,0.049560547,-0.012336731,0.0006260872,0.020980835,-0.009185791,0.0087890625,-0.040252686,-0.017089844,-0.008644104,-0.024215698,0.020523071,0.06210327,-0.027160645,-0.008583069,0.058013916,0.05355835,-0.022003174,-0.012557983,-0.015655518,0.02357483,-0.016174316,0.02027893,0.076293945,-0.00032401085,0.020187378,0.020935059,-0.009216309,0.010032654,-0.03564453,0.022583008,-0.07244873,-0.007408142,0.0084991455,0.015808105,-0.035858154,0.01940918,-0.010009766,0.01687622,0.009475708,0.010124207,-0.006149292,0.0047073364,-0.0018196106,-0.033172607,0.0