(2173,	NULL,	NULL,	'Durante más de un año, el Departamento articulado con la facultad de Ingeniería lideró un proceso de evaluación institucional con la participación de estudiantes, docentes y directivos académicos. El objetivo fue identificar el impacto real, la pertinencia y los vacíos en la actual oferta formativa en informática. Entre los hallazgos más significativos se destacan los siguientes:
80% de los estudiantes consideran que los contenidos representan una repetición de lo aprendido en la educación media.
60% afirman que las evaluaciones se centran en el reconocimiento de menús y comandos, sin evaluar habilidades aplicadas ni resolución de problemas reales.
70% cuestionan la utilidad práctica de los cursos, especialmente en su modalidad virtual, la cual utiliza versiones desactualizadas de las herramientas (Word, Excel, PowerPoint).
95% sugieren incluir opciones más modernas, alineadas con herramientas, plataformas y contextos reales del entorno laboral y académico.',	'[-0.05407715,0.027450562,0.042938232,-0.0115737915,0.027618408,0.015129089,0.0054130554,0.037506104,-0.0067253113,0.05432129,0.022872925,-0.046447754,-0.018463135,-0.017028809,-0.014602661,0.03982544,-0.011772156,-0.022476196,-0.0051193237,-0.0038433075,0.036712646,-0.01247406,0.001156807,0.01247406,0.0065460205,-0.021957397,0.000790596,0.026428223,-0.027679443,-0.014198303,0.0052261353,-0.02861023,0.0038414001,-0.0029697418,-0.004306793,0.012580872,-0.0064086914,0.023147583,0.04611206,-0.045959473,0.01713562,0.061309814,-0.0048065186,-0.006706238,-0.031219482,-0.028442383,0.008346558,-0.0090789795,0.05618286,0.039794922,-0.062438965,0.02885437,0.08087158,0.014984131,0.0113220215,-0.018127441,-0.04800415,-0.017974854,-0.011810303,-0.014533997,0.048614502,-0.01977539,0.04562378,0.03616333,0.000702858,-0.014587402,-0.021896362,0.013305664,-0.0076522827,0.016738892,0.01727295,0.021697998,0.0052871704,0.011734009,-0.02180481,0.04611206,0.02784729,-0.010658264,-0.0029678345,0.043670654,0.018508911,0.00084638596,0.0010995865,-0.028793335,0.015655518,0.021408081,-0.053619385,-0.033599854,-0.029129028,-0.022323608,-0.044128418,0.03744507,-0.010009766,0.015388489,-0.0033359528,0.011459351,5.4836273e-05,-0.013298035,-0.012084961,0.029632568,-0.013053894,-0.006877899,0.016601562,0.00957489,0.026260376,-0.04815674,0.009239197,-0.0178833,-0.0063552856,-0.005531311,0.021759033,-0.027923584,-0.032592773,-0.007080078,0.013008118,-0.029891968,-0.01335144,-0.046173096,-0.010627747,-0.011352539,-0.029464722,0.0048980713,-0.050079346,0.017944336,0.011222839,-0.05065918,0.011756897,0.035827637,0.0011377335,-0.05758667,-0.036071777,-0.009490967,0.036376953,-0.015975952,-0.045074463,0.013900757,-0.016998291,0.012016296,-0.022918701,0.00042653084,0.011436462,-0.006313324,-0.042419434,0.020339966,-0.023468018,-0.015266418,0.036315918,0.026138306,0.057586