(2175,	NULL,	NULL,	'En muchos casos, programan sus propios cursos o establecen procesos de homologación o validación independientes, lo que genera inconsistencias y fragmentación en la formación digital institucional.
Mientras que en los programas presenciales y virtuales los cursos de informática no tienen asignación de créditos académicos, en los programas de T&T y Dual sí forman parte formal del plan de estudios. Sin embargo, no existe una propuesta integral y contextualizada que responda a las necesidades específicas del estudiante técnico o del profesional en formación dual, ni al ritmo acelerado de cambio en las habilidades requeridas en la industria y el entorno digital.
Estos resultados demuestran que el modelo actual carece de cohesión institucional, presenta limitaciones pedagógicas y tecnológicas, y no responde adecuadamente ni a las expectativas de los estudiantes ni a las tendencias globales en educación digital.',	'[-0.01751709,0.03475952,0.03967285,-0.0056266785,0.03074646,0.009231567,0.07867432,0.024276733,-0.0033302307,0.020858765,0.016983032,0.017532349,0.0074043274,-0.01826477,-0.039520264,-0.014312744,-0.007904053,-0.010467529,0.044006348,0.051757812,-0.0006222725,-0.026657104,-0.0039405823,-5.38826e-05,0.016616821,-0.044891357,0.018157959,0.04309082,-0.029281616,0.028671265,0.042755127,-0.031280518,-0.021072388,-0.028366089,0.03274536,0.033599854,-0.0023956299,0.090148926,0.029464722,0.011199951,-0.009979248,0.02407837,-0.041748047,0.016906738,-0.042144775,-0.01751709,0.0057754517,-0.012542725,0.01159668,0.042999268,-0.008255005,0.0018520355,0.024215698,0.04498291,-0.010467529,-0.009132385,-0.044311523,-0.016799927,-0.017150879,-0.022705078,0.06842041,0.009483337,0.040924072,0.037750244,0.015396118,0.021026611,-0.04864502,-0.026550293,-0.057250977,-0.00066900253,-0.015686035,-0.011634827,0.0018453598,0.020065308,0.002532959,0.042785645,0.009094238,0.018615723,0.01625061,0.04550171,0.023727417,0.00705719,-0.0018939972,-0.021255493,0.015304565,0.052612305,-0.05996704,-0.0423584,-0.025299072,-0.02142334,-0.022399902,0.04208374,-0.040527344,0.051605225,0.0059013367,0.0072669983,0.022872925,-0.0069618225,0.01802063,0.0038795471,-0.012031555,-0.011054993,0.0033130646,-0.0012626648,0.027145386,-0.040924072,-0.022918701,0.007167816,-0.04168701,0.0019798279,0.044403076,0.0007634163,0.02659607,-0.040771484,0.033111572,-0.09124756,-0.00082206726,-0.0060920715,-0.025177002,0.006248474,-0.02192688,-0.0046424866,-0.039642334,0.015625,-0.012466431,-0.030334473,-0.0029392242,0.00957489,-0.031143188,-0.04598999,-0.03173828,-0.009284973,-0.021026611,0.0027446747,-0.04147339,-0.008033752,-0.045013428,0.0034370422,0.0029792786,-0.02580261