(2181,	NULL,	NULL,	'Tecnología y aprendizaje digital: el siglo XXI ha visto una revolución tecnológica sin precedentes, y la UNAB no ha sido ajena a esta transformación. La introducción de plataformas de aprendizaje digital, la expansión de recursos en línea y la integración de tecnologías emergentes han optimizado la experiencia educativa. Este hito ha ubicado a la Universidad a la vanguardia de la educación digital, al permitir a estudiantes y docentes aprovechar al máximo las herramientas disponibles para potenciar el aprendizaje y la colaboración.',	'[-0.013954163,-0.017532349,0.021133423,-7.4625015e-05,0.023284912,0.009506226,0.019561768,0.060821533,-0.033081055,0.020599365,0.013191223,-0.029190063,-0.041931152,-0.00274086,0.01763916,0.045288086,0.0009198189,-0.0128479,0.009391785,0.013053894,0.008476257,-0.053985596,0.013519287,-0.013130188,0.015403748,-0.028045654,0.0035572052,0.035858154,-0.06591797,-0.00623703,0.0033607483,-0.02722168,-0.0132751465,0.0065841675,0.007633209,0.03112793,-0.013053894,0.028137207,-0.0023460388,-0.02255249,-0.0032310486,-0.016479492,0.03253174,0.007987976,-0.05328369,0.003856659,-0.019882202,-0.041625977,0.017471313,0.06149292,-0.05114746,-0.0026054382,0.01802063,-0.00061130524,-0.013793945,-0.016967773,0.018371582,-0.0034275055,-0.010925293,-0.01158905,0.0067214966,0.05706787,0.040527344,0.053497314,0.042175293,-0.04309082,-0.029281616,0.020553589,-0.08270264,-0.033111572,0.011169434,-0.02053833,-0.033172607,0.00579834,-0.043792725,0.034210205,0.015411377,0.021728516,-0.031982422,-0.027435303,0.008598328,-0.01902771,-0.013679504,-0.02494812,0.002046585,0.042388916,-0.026733398,-0.029449463,-0.030227661,0.008743286,0.0039482117,0.006668091,-0.040985107,0.047943115,-0.0031490326,0.04486084,0.020401001,-0.036590576,0.046905518,0.028076172,0.0004723072,-0.031234741,0.021850586,-0.034332275,-0.0138549805,-0.06210327,-0.016708374,-0.062683105,0.0017366409,0.009437561,-0.024002075,-0.052337646,-0.00034618378,-0.004508972,0.019302368,-0