(2182,	NULL,	NULL,	'En conclusión, la evolución del PEI de la UNAB refleja una trayectoria de adaptación a los cambios sociales, tecnológicos y globales. Desde 1962, la institución ha mantenido una firme filosofía centrada en la formación integral y la autonomía, pero ha sabido ajustarse a las demandas de cada época. La investigación, la internacionalización y la incorporación de la estética como un elemento clave demuestran el compromiso con la calidad educativa en un mundo en constante evolución.
Los cambios vertiginosos en las tecnologías, la automatización del trabajo y el avance de la inteligencia artificial hacen inviable mantener una oferta formativa estática, basada únicamente en herramientas tradicionales. Es urgente una transición hacia un modelo flexible, actualizado y centrado en el estudiante, que ofrezca:
Cursos modulares por niveles y temáticas emergentes (IA, Gestión de contenidos, ciudadanía digital, análisis de datos, ciberseguridad).',	'[0.012260437,0.02532959,0.055145264,0.010658264,0.026779175,0.014511108,0.031158447,0.08502197,-0.007686615,0.018753052,0.039489746,-0.032073975,-0.026382446,-0.018859863,-0.005428314,0.042755127,0.02671814,-0.034179688,-0.021240234,0.035369873,0.016342163,-0.052246094,0.0082473755,0.013969421,0.0035037994,-0.032226562,0.026428223,0.06359863,-0.04751587,0.004383087,0.04373169,-0.012916565,-0.012207031,0.008560181,-0.044128418,0.025680542,-0.04562378,0.029846191,0.025527954,-0.028335571,0.009346008,0.007534027,0.0017938614,0.010910034,-0.064331055,-0.0057258606,-0.008224487,0.006958008,0.022964478,0.049224854,-0.037322998,0.012832642,0.06188965,0.0036811829,-0.0037117004,-0.0061149597,-0.010948181,-0.027694702,-0.00630188,0.009635925,0.053741455,0.016220093,0.052886963,0.038513184,-0.0006685257,-0.022521973,-0.045806885,0.041381836,-0.06524658,-0.029647827,0.019836426,-0.0345459,-0.019012451,-0.0046081543,-0.0446167,0.041931152,0.01576233,0.0011110306,-0.020721436,-0.0031166077,-0.010269165,0.0020046234,0.01586914,-0.013786316,0.01838684,0.026123047,-0.04107666,-0.040008545,-0.046936035,-0.01260376,-0.051452637,0.019210815,-0.04562378,0.013923645,0.014350891,0.01828003,0.0073242188,-0.05166626,0.02658081,0.036376953,-0.021865845,-0.01777649,-0.0047912598,-0.045715332,0.009933472,-0.03378296,0.008934021,-0.02482605,-0.059906006,0.00409317,-0.009063721,-0.043823242,0.012588501,0.032928467,0.018432617,-0.07537842,-0.013694763,-0.007007599,-0.014717102,0.0115356445,0.0055999756,-0.027069092,-0.0014591217,0.008018494,0.02331543,-0.054229736,0.012557983,0.014099121,-0.048309326,-0.051818848,0.0044059753,0.0058898926,-0.021972656,-0.016464233,-0.0065193176,-0.0236969,0.00680542,-0.0032196045,-0.0031261444,-0.052337646,0.030654907,0.0029754639,-0.064575195,0.022094727,-0.049560547,0.015174866,-0.007896423,0.03555298,0.11437988,0.042266846