(2185,	NULL,	NULL,	'La transformación de la oferta de formación de informática hacia competencias digitales no puede limitarse a una actualización de contenidos o metodologías: requiere también un cambio en la identidad institucional del área responsable. Por esta razón, se propone reemplazar el actual nombre “Departamento de Informática” por Departamento de Competencias Digitales (DCD), lo que representa con mayor fidelidad los nuevos objetivos, enfoques y alcances de su acción dentro de la Universidad Autónoma de Bucaramanga.
Este cambio es coherente con la redefinición global del concepto de competencias digitales, entendido no como la simple capacidad de operar herramientas ofimáticas, sino como el conjunto de habilidades, conocimientos, actitudes y valores que permiten participar de forma activa, crítica y responsable en entornos digitales complejos.
De acuerdo con el Marco Europeo de Competencias Digitales para la Ciudadanía (DigComp 2.2), las áreas clave de las competencias digitales son:',	'[0.04562378,-0.03366089,0.03277588,0.02331543,0.0020885468,0.0036125183,0.049591064,0.04336548,-0.004749298,-0.021057129,0.030975342,-0.019699097,-0.0074768066,-0.057861328,0.025650024,0.04864502,0.0017995834,-0.0051116943,0.01727295,0.028076172,0.018325806,-0.060394287,0.014465332,0.05331421,-0.0036563873,-0.014755249,-0.009376526,0.019851685,-0.023330688,-0.02255249,0.016677856,-0.032806396,-0.020019531,-0.033111572,0.049682617,0.048339844,-0.053955078,0.059387207,0.030090332,-0.0069465637,0.017089844,0.0040283203,-0.020217896,-0.027954102,-0.04348755,-0.008773804,-0.009101868,-0.015899658,0.04296875,0.019195557,-0.025543213,0.012161255,0.049591064,0.020507812,-0.017913818,0.049468994,-0.017532349,0.0014686584,-0.002073288,0.022415161,0.025344849,-0.032684326,0.030136108,0.0005965233,-0.004535675,0.017196655,-0.052124023,0.015602112,-0.028137207,-0.027069092,0.024749756,0.05206299,-0.0124435425,-0.0017499924,-0.009567261,0.032165527,0.015197754,0.015129089,-0.02671814,0.009262085,-0.02519226,-0.027328491,0.053833008,-0.056488037,-0.012512207,0.024795532,-0.037506104,-0.035003662,-0.0026016235,-0.021026611,-0.00894928,0.014625549,-0.055786133,-0.004371643,-0.0395813,0.008522034,-0.0002424717,-0.022949219,0.0069732666,0.05871582,0.0034160614,-0.027023315,0.037841797,-0.008895874,0.0025978088,-0.016586304,0.0004413128,-0.015335083,-0.02911377,-0.015274048,-0.0012741089,0.00031399727,0.022399902,0.0184021,0.026031494,-0.06854248,-0.010681152,-0.02230835,-0.0045776367,-0.035980225,0.013931274,-0.03149414,-0.03111267,-0.016616821,-0.03289795,-0.033355713,0.04989624,0.024765015,-0.04232788,-0.06365967,-0.01574707,-0.03933716,-0.02923584,-0.008468628,0.0079574585,-0.031677246,-0.059265137,-0.006378174,-0.0140686035,-0.024169922,-0.0059547424,-0.022094727,-0.010131836,-0.011459351,-0.032287598,-0.026123047,-0.011749268,0.06915283