(2186,	NULL,	NULL,	'De acuerdo con el Marco Europeo de Competencias Digitales para la Ciudadanía (DigComp 2.2), las áreas clave de las competencias digitales son:
Alfabetización en información y datos
Comunicación y colaboración digital
Creación de contenido digital
Seguridad digital
Resolución de problemas y aprendizaje autónomo en entornos tecnológicos
Estas dimensiones van más allá de la operación básica de software, involucrando habilidades como el pensamiento computacional, el uso ético de la inteligencia artificial, la ciberseguridad, el trabajo colaborativo en red y la creación de soluciones digitales. Por tanto, la identidad y el propósito del nuevo departamento deben alinearse a este marco internacional, así como a las aspiraciones del nuevo Proyecto Educativo Institucional (PEI) de la UNAB.',	'[0.040008545,0.010910034,0.055633545,0.036743164,0.027862549,0.01235199,0.040252686,0.06829834,-0.025421143,0.015068054,0.010246277,-0.02041626,-0.0010852814,-0.053375244,0.01802063,0.044555664,-0.028137207,-0.030975342,0.038604736,0.034240723,0.04058838,-0.058135986,0.006904602,0.01474762,-0.025436401,0.0038070679,-0.006652832,0.046051025,-0.04019165,0.003610611,0.00548172,-0.037017822,-0.010353088,-0.023345947,0.043701172,-0.0058555603,-0.059936523,0.0597229,-0.008117676,-0.010787964,0.0012712479,-0.011833191,0.00062942505,-0.016143799,-0.09295654,-0.014907837,-0.022262573,-0.0027637482,0.03768921,0.04434204,-0.027252197,-0.0026664734,0.0769043,0.052978516,-0.03918457,0.03463745,-0.012329102,-0.015701294,-0.022033691,0.019683838,0.033416748,-0.0046310425,0.023635864,0.023452759,0.011993408,0.0033493042,-0.011505127,0.011001587,-0.045562744,-0.04171753,0.030670166,0.041107178,0.0012969971,-0.020690918,-0.025161743,0.01473999,0.018981934,0.028823853,-0.03012085,-0.012260437,-0.01209259,-0.021209717,0.027435303,-0.027786255,-0.021057129,0.03564453,-0.050109863,-0.04888916,-0.019836426,-0.022109985,-0.06524658,0.0060691833,-0.04144287,0.013542175,-0.0140686035,0.0007739067,0.003332138,-0.031204224,0.010131836,0.035491943,-0.022857666,-0.029922485,0.009750366,-0.022567749,-0.017578125,-0.02017212,-0.018371582,-0.03353882,0.012168884,-0.0051727295,-0.024337769,-0.014640808,0.010467529,0.03137207,0.04547119,-0.08026123,-0.039886475,-0.046020508,-0.017730713,-0.013534546,0.0026931763,-0.012863159,-0.03869629,-0.0030822754,