(2188,	NULL,	NULL,	'La propuesta del DCD está profundamente alineada con la visión del PEI actualizado y especialmente con los seis desafíos que orientan la transformación del componente sociohumanístico, entre los cuales el desarrollo tecnológico acelerado ocupa un lugar central. El DCD contribuirá también directamente a:
Formar ciudadanos digitales éticos y críticos, preparados para comprender y actuar frente a la inteligencia artificial, la desinformación, la automatización y la vigilancia digital.
Articular la formación tecnológica con valores como la equidad, la justicia social, la sostenibilidad y la libertad individual.
Desarrollar habilidades ciudadanas para el siglo XXI, tales como:
Apropiación crítica de tecnologías
Inteligencia emocional y trabajo colaborativo en entornos digitales
Pensamiento innovador y creatividad digital
Convivencia democrática en redes sociales
Conciencia ambiental aplicada a contextos tecnológicos',	'[0.073791504,0.012466431,0.015914917,0.03857422,0.043548584,-0.0006828308,0.03491211,0.0982666,-0.049438477,0.03829956,0.038330078,-0.0135269165,-0.007205963,-0.027770996,0.0018348694,0.008125305,-0.020446777,-0.033325195,0.056365967,0.03479004,0.003068924,0.0067443848,0.009613037,0.024017334,-0.014091492,-0.005470276,0.027496338,0.03717041,-0.030181885,0.02734375,-0.0074386597,-0.024246216,-0.036346436,-0.019577026,0.032470703,0.013374329,-0.05316162,0.057006836,0.007419586,0.011528015,0.02772522,-0.018112183,-0.014213562,-0.0129776,-0.06188965,-0.061828613,0.014450073,-0.008163452,0.025985718,0.049224854,0.017028809,0.022079468,0.0496521,0.06604004,-0.03439331,0.00831604,-0.04272461,0.0009174347,-0.029632568,0.06414795,0.074157715,-0.0016155243,0.009292603,0.024887085,-0.012039185,0.022720337,-0.037353516,0.023483276,-0.0070877075,-0.019470215,0.008300781,0.032989502,0.004863739,-0.032440186,-0.009971619,-0.0013589859,0.0066223145,-0.014129639,-0.029571533,0.006088257,-0.011383057,-0.02456665,-0.020843506,0.023620605,0.0022010803,-0.020751953,-0.03149414,-0.05026245,-0.039031982,-0.0019168854,-0.038360596,-0.001159668,-0.048217773,-0.0056915283,-0.02192688,0.027435303,0.02482605,-0.00079250336,0.027053833,0.028747559,0.010902405,-0.012069702,0.0062675476,-0.0033855438,-0.005004883,-0.020492554,0.010368347,-0.015930176,-0.011398315,-0.0032577515,0.0008378029,0.022338867,0.012229919,0.0748291,0.0413208,-0.0758667,-0.043395996,0.0048942566,0.012458801,-0.0014410019,-0.016326904,-0.027389526,-0.06329346,0.034729004,-0.030807495,-0.070007324,0.010063171,-0.026733398,-0.06628418,-0.027938843,0.0026855469,0.053527832,0.009613037,0.0022239685,0.02067566,-0.01965332,-0.0418396,0.010757446,-0.020706177,-0.06604004,0.012748718,-0.025253296,0.0046157837,0.0099487305,-0.00032520294,-0.03189087,0.0209198,0.011360168,0.00014948845,0.07086182,-0.024887085,0.0035247803,0.003692627,0.0046653748,-0.0056533813,-0.012702942,0.0