(2189,	NULL,	NULL,	'Pensamiento innovador y creatividad digital
Convivencia democrática en redes sociales
Conciencia ambiental aplicada a contextos tecnológicos
De esta forma, el DCD se convierte no solo en un proveedor de cursos técnicos, sino en un actor clave para el desarrollo integral del estudiante UNAB, en coherencia con la misión de formar profesionales éticos, críticos, innovadores y comprometidos con la transformación del entorno.',	'[0.052368164,0.011436462,0.02482605,0.055908203,0.023025513,-0.015075684,0.049865723,0.07476807,-0.029632568,0.02961731,0.032073975,0.004737854,-0.027633667,-0.012260437,0.039093018,0.04724121,-0.048583984,-0.036254883,0.03302002,0.059570312,0.00617218,-0.03527832,0.040405273,0.033050537,0.0050239563,-0.008674622,0.010772705,0.046417236,-0.024902344,-0.012001038,0.011627197,-0.025680542,-0.048217773,-0.038238525,0.0007004738,0.03817749,0.00033688545,0.03366089,-0.0084991455,0.003868103,-0.0034656525,-0.021331787,0.012580872,0.010948181,-0.03010559,-0.0423584,-0.025924683,0.00945282,0.035247803,0.036071777,-0.028182983,0.05114746,0.06524658,0.014709473,-0.044708252,-0.020736694,-0.051696777,-0.014152527,-0.005508423,0.010116577,0.041015625,0.0026416779,0.014968872,0.045654297,0.024368286,0.0058631897,-0.049987793,0.024475098,-0.050994873,-0.0368042,0.02861023,-0.0103302,-0.0046844482,-0.035949707,-0.027893066,0.015213013,0.027679443,-0.023635864,-0.027526855,-0.021026611,0.008956909,0.036071777,0.0036087036,0.0013046265,-0.016998291,-0.030410767,-0.06124878,-0.05230713,-0.023712158,0.015129089,-0.00093221664,0.013053894,-0.037841797,0.043640137,0.012992859,0.043060303,0.0039367676,-0.010543823,0.023666382,0.023880005,0.0038013458,-0.0056533813,0.01751709,-0.022521973,-0.02204895,-0.036712646,-0.0070533752,-0.043701172,-0.022720337,0.024520874,0.015701294,-0.019592285,0.028717041,0.035369873,0.029510498,-0.08905029,-0.0074272156,-0.049468994,-0.006046295,-0.0027942657,-0.025161743,-0.01838684,-0.047210693,0.010803223,-0.02319336,-0.05279541,-0.007381439,0.0014533997,-0.05847168,-0.041870117,0.0037021637,0.05871582,-0.020080566,-0.023635864,0.009986877,-0.02784729,-0.051879883,-0.0031280