(2191,	NULL,	NULL,	'El análisis interno de la operación del actual Departamento de Informática evidencia múltiples limitaciones que confirman la necesidad urgente de transformación:
Baja visibilidad y liderazgo institucional.
Oferta fragmentada, centrada exclusivamente en herramientas como Word, Excel y PowerPoint, sin una ruta de aprendizaje estructurada ni progresiva.
Modelos obsoletos, con contenidos repetitivos, versiones de software desactualizadas y carencia de conexión con tecnologías emergentes (IA, interacción Digital, Gestión de Contenido, ciudadanía digital, entre otras).
Desarticulación con los programas académicos, especialmente en los programas de T&T y modalidad Dual, donde se programan cursos propios sin una propuesta integral y donde los cursos tienen créditos académicos, pero no relevancia disciplinar.
Falta de conexión con las necesidades de los futuros profesionales, procesos de empleabilidad y competencias reales demandadas por el entorno laboral.',	'[-0.039031982,0.039855957,0.05618286,-0.0077819824,0.032287598,0.012084961,0.047607422,0.05114746,-0.030319214,0.017593384,0.0096588135,-0.044311523,-0.012367249,-0.033691406,-0.012435913,0.014572144,0.015991211,-0.02684021,0.016738892,0.03338623,0.0362854,-0.023910522,-0.008125305,0.029052734,0.0073394775,0.00016415119,-0.028930664,0.013046265,-0.015701294,0.00056505203,0.04498291,-0.024871826,0.00014603138,-0.0037250519,0.032684326,0.02305603,-0.008277893,0.066833496,0.053527832,-0.0152282715,0.0045204163,0.02720642,0.0026340485,0.016052246,-0.008872986,-0.028442383,-0.0059280396,-0.010620117,0.03677368,0.029449463,-0.049987793,0.0124053955,0.061553955,0.030899048,-0.014877319,-0.0138168335,-0.013755798,-0.03918457,-0.032165527,0.00032687187,0.049468994,-0.009689331,0.030029297,0.062408447,-0.017745972,-0.026443481,-0.03677368,0.02330017,-0.027694702,-0.022338867,0.0046577454,0.025222778,-0.01322937,-0.0050964355,-0.015403748,0.04196167,0.01586914,-0.013374329,-0.0020561218,0.045928955,0.0050811768,-0.008369446,0.015533447,-0.02067566,-0.0035934448,0.021972656,-0.056427002,-0.047027588,-0.049987793,-0.051208496,-0.023605347,0.046417236,-0.03668213,0.002456665,-0.017089844,0.017303467,-0.002067566,0.012008667,0.006175995,0.040374756,0.011177063,-0.025131226,0.026885986,-0.019882202,-0.012825012,-0.058563232,0.01953125,-0.059936523,-0.033416748,0.022659302,-0.0051078796,-0.046813965,-0.0020942688,-0.001865387,0.020324707,-0.04135132,-0.017837524,-0.013442993,0.008674622,0.0025749207,-0.00086927414,-0.00617218,-0.06390381,0.04537964,-0.015426636,-0.04562378,0.03036499,0.010177612,-0.024612427,-0.059753418,-0.0037631989,-0.025802612,-0.011428833,-0.025177002,-0.031311035,-0.009819031,-0.03665161,0.020385742,0.0055732727,0.012611389,0.020370483,0.006248474,-0.026245117,0.025482178,-0.057739258,0.00026798248,0.03189087