(2194,	NULL,	NULL,	'La transformación de los contenidos exige también una transformación del marco institucional desde el cual se diseñan, gestionan y evalúan. No basta con cambiar los cursos: se debe cambiar el enfoque, la estructura, los objetivos y el nombre del departamento.
El nuevo Departamento de Competencias  Digitales(DCD) responderá a los desafíos contemporáneos con una oferta formativa moderna, ética, dinámica y alineada al PEI. No se trata solo de enseñar software, sino de formar personas capaces de comprender, crear y transformar con tecnología en contextos reales y cambiantes.
Este enfoque permitirá que el DCD:
Lidere la formación transversal en habilidades digitales tanto para estudiantes como para docentes y administrativos.
Desarrolle rutas de formación personalizadas y electivas con énfasis en inteligencia artificial, automatización, analítica, ciudadanía digital, programación y seguridad.
Apoye procesos de transformación curricular en pregrado, posgrado y extensión.',	'[0.02583313,0.0072402954,0.042938232,0.008911133,0.045166016,-0.0039482117,0.07110596,0.072753906,-0.025756836,0.017150879,0.06347656,-0.042877197,-0.009803772,-0.025436401,0.009231567,0.035614014,0.006690979,-0.034362793,0.042022705,0.027130127,0.017242432,-0.052703857,0.026473999,0.028915405,0.014328003,-0.0012798309,0.013809204,0.023742676,-0.022750854,0.0037994385,0.023513794,-0.019638062,-0.050750732,-0.019226074,0.057403564,0.009208679,-0.055480957,0.0803833,0.03579712,-0.027999878,0.011016846,0.014587402,-0.022735596,-0.016433716,-0.04763794,-0.022094727,-0.010215759,-0.011398315,0.04547119,0.058410645,0.0015583038,0.030288696,0.05609131,0.05078125,-0.019485474,0.04058838,-0.018692017,-0.010261536,-0.021194458,0.00970459,0.060577393,-0.0236969,0.00932312,0.034057617,0.021011353,0.03274536,-0.06518555,0.009155273,-0.030319214,-0.021087646,0.032806396,0.030319214,-0.0109939575,-0.016174316,-0.033721924,0.010139465,0.00687027,0.018035889,-0.02708435,0.018951416,-0.007255554,-0.032440186,0.015914917,-0.02142334,-0.015289307,0.02798462,-0.035064697,-0.03363037,-0.019714355,-0.02519226,-0.021087646,-0.0061683655,-0.058441162,0.004009247,-0.026138306,0.028808594,-0.005645752,0.0062408447,0.00472641,0.04168701,0.023040771,-0.03173828,0.035125732,0.007736206,-0.012611389,-0.03692627,-0.0181427,-0.006893158,-0.060058594,-0.0046424866,-0.015037537,-0.011550903,0.022140503,0.014762878,0.040405273,-0.06677246,0.0124053955,-0.02458191,-0.022216797,-0.01626587,-0.025482178,0.0004954338,-0.04800415,-0.0050239563,-0.015792847,-0.04244995,0.016616821,-0.0084991455,-0.041137695,-0.041259766,-0.0040245056,-0.009185791,-0.002878189,-0.028045654,-0.00920105,-0.010772705,-0.057922363,-0.005580902,-0.018432617,-0.035980225,0.028045654,-0.02508545,-0.029907227,0.024719238,-0.047851562,-0.049316406,-0.0069084167,0.057800293,0.04260254,0.052734375,-0.02557373,-0.027328491,-0.059661865,0.0007548332,0.00389