(2196,	NULL,	NULL,	'## Objetivos propuestos para el DCD

Responder a las exigencias del PEI de la UNAB, en especial el ítem 1.8.6 sobre Competencia Tecnológica.
Articularse con los modelos de ciclos de formación: común, mayor y menor.
Asumir un rol visible y de liderazgo académico en el desarrollo de competencias digitales institucionales.
Diseñar e implementar rutas flexibles y actualizadas de formación en habilidades digitales, con posibilidad de certificación interna o externa.
Fortalecer la calidad de todos los programas académicos, brindando herramientas digitales pertinentes y diferenciadas por disciplina.
Impactar en los ejes misionales: docencia, investigación, extensión y proyección social.
Desarrollar un plan de transición estructurado y participativo, que permita la adopción gradual de los nuevos cursos y enfoques.

## Líneas de acción del DCD',	'[0.034088135,0.019119263,0.047332764,0.017974854,-0.011482239,0.02961731,0.03555298,0.08605957,-0.019973755,0.008728027,0.034606934,-0.016601562,-0.04714966,-0.036590576,-0.0024967194,0.024124146,-0.009223938,0.004878998,0.025161743,0.055145264,0.030731201,-0.046844482,0.019760132,0.033111572,-0.0016765594,-0.019454956,0.037384033,0.043060303,-0.015167236,-0.03286743,0.013771057,-0.028640747,-0.056793213,-0.01889038,0.019607544,0.027145386,-0.052947998,0.07647705,-0.011787415,-0.004131317,0.017578125,-0.002084732,-0.0060424805,-0.037139893,-0.07281494,-0.027252197,-0.02166748,0.004875183,0.04135132,0.03326416,0.009689331,0.05606079,0.06713867,0.029663086,-0.046905518,0.017486572,-0.0039367676,-0.024002075,-0.016998291,0.022872925,0.04067993,-0.003326416,0.017120361,0.031280518,0.017303467,0.012374878,-0.043823242,0.016403198,-0.014640808,-0.028320312,0.0025691986,0.015434265,-0.018341064,-0.024307251,-0.010047913,-0.0020008087,0.0030078888,-0.017242432,-0.032928467,0.024368286,-0.014640808,0.008911133,0.015914917,-0.027038574,-0.00052690506,-0.025466919,-0.04034424,-0.0418396,-0.038330078,-0.01222229,-0.048919678,-0.0023765564,-0.055145264,0.019195557,0.02609253,0.005935669,0.014709473,-0.023040771,0.031234741,0.034698486,0.014442444,-0.02810669,0.022964478,-0.048919678,-0.018630981,-0.015426636,-0.028305054,-0.010063171,-0.014083862,0.002357483,0.024871826,0.002521515,0.023010254,0.037872314,0.04977417,-0.07751465,-0.036895752,-0.034606934,-0.018173218,-0.015808105,-0.026748657,-0.0035686493,-0.029663086,-0.016220093,-0.0017089844,-0.04916382,0.016647339,-0.003944397,-0.051971436,-0.04135132,-0.009132385,0.009109497,0.01751709,-0.036102295,0.010482788,-0.0066223145,-0.042175293,-0.0016870499,-0.03213501,-0.051116943,0.03753662,-0.009819031,-0.0037269592,0.014808655,-0.011108398,-0.027542114,0.02053833,0.012367249,0.035614014,0.04333496,-0.05355835,-0.0012798309,-0.017471313,-0.0357666,0.008766174,0.0007839203,-0.05380249,0.019866943,0