(2199,	NULL,	NULL,	'Figura 2. Ruta de competencias digitales
Fuente: Elaboración propia.
En la gráfica anterior se observan los pilares y los cursos, que vamos a desarrollar más adelante, las principales características de ruta de formación son:
Hacen parte de la formación transversal y del ciclo común de los programas académicos de la UNAB. No tienen asignación de créditos en los programas de pregrado profesional universitario en modalidad presencial y virtual.
El primer curso, correspondiente al pilar de Competencias Digitales Básicas, es común y obligatorio para todos los estudiantes.
En los demás pilares, el estudiante deberá cursar uno solo por cada pilar.
Los cursos no tienen prerrequisitos y pueden ser reconocidos mediante  credenciales alternativas o certificaciones  siempre que cumpla con los lineamientos institucionales para reconocimiento de aprendizaje.
El estudiante que complete la ruta de formación recibirá por parte de la UNAB una insignia en "Competencias Digitales".',	'[-0.011520386,0.039001465,0.054840088,-0.005214691,-0.005962372,-0.006538391,0.044799805,0.040252686,-0.0038223267,0.026138306,0.027816772,-0.03125,0.0012836456,-0.040740967,-0.0050239563,0.04309082,-0.016937256,-0.035125732,-0.0029258728,0.07623291,0.059417725,-0.061584473,0.010398865,0.023956299,-0.008277893,-0.017578125,0.041656494,0.03894043,-0.0519104,0.019088745,0.004119873,-0.029129028,0.00422287,-0.009880066,0.02357483,0.015274048,-0.029754639,0.089904785,-0.0043563843,0.0014257431,0.010520935,0.018966675,-0.011314392,-0.03741455,-0.07550049,0.0056915283,0.0065078735,0.0026493073,0.016433716,0.06549072,-0.054504395,0.0259552,0.049987793,0.031204224,-0.05987549,-0.00096797943,-0.012329102,-0.037078857,-0.016540527,-0.02532959,0.03955078,0.01448822,0.011993408,0.011299133,0.05328369,0.024642944,-0.03945923,0.021316528,-0.017242432,-0.004432678,0.008811951,-0.015472412,0.028503418,0.004589081,-0.0018701553,0.046813965,0.029190063,0.014389038,-0.0178833,-0.022720337,-0.0032978058,0.009857178,0.041137695,-0.060791016,-0.0052452087,-0.009757996,-0.0690918,-0.049041748,0.0031700134,-0.0041007996,-0.0058898926,-0.019577026,-0.062347412,0.062805176,0.027694702,0.030258179,0.03793335,-0.013702393,0.014533997,0.009635925,0.017074585,-0.037017822,0.001077652,-0.016571045,-0.0019140244,-0.033721924,-0.020431519,0.012863159,-0.028961182,-0.00074768066,0.022354126,0.006538391,0.041503906,0.013381958,0.07476807,-0.053894043,-0.014541626,-0.02999878,-0.040863037,-0.01184845,-0.006713867,-0.015640259,-0.024246216,-0.019744873,-0.041259766,-0.04425049,0.028045654,0.02619934,-0.052764893,-0.058685303,-0.03353882,-0.02217102,0.020736694,-0.026306152,0.002248764,-0.0045547485,-0.014274597,-0.019241333,-0.01586914,-0.02180481,0.0020885468,-0.016113281,-0.017684937,0.040649414,-0.04586792,-0.015174866,0.0035552979,0.053588867,0.04446411,0.008178711,-0.03579712,