(2210,	NULL,	NULL,	'RAE 2:
Analiza un caso real o hipotético relacionado con el uso de tecnología (ej. recolección de datos, desinformación, ciberacoso), identificando las implicaciones legales y éticas para los involucrados a la luz de la normativa vigente y los principios de derechos digitales, para formular una postura argumentada.
RAE 3:
Diseña un plan de acción personal para gestionar su bienestar digital, a partir de un autodiagnóstico de sus hábitos tecnológicos (tiempo de pantalla, consumo de información, interacciones en redes), para fomentar un equilibrio saludable entre la vida conectada y desconectada y mitigar riesgos como la fatiga digital o la sobrecarga de información.
Correspondencia con DigComp:
Área 1: Alfabetización en información y datos
Área 4: Seguridad digital
Área 5: Resolución de problemas',	'[0.047302246,0.04525757,0.03677368,0.008903503,0.01826477,-0.007331848,0.0067596436,0.03768921,0.0030841827,0.055023193,0.034301758,-0.013839722,0.017150879,-0.049224854,0.014915466,-0.0049591064,-0.04244995,-0.029342651,0.016235352,0.050720215,0.039489746,0.014137268,0.03765869,0.01373291,0.021636963,0.014472961,0.038391113,0.045898438,-0.013710022,-0.015579224,0.005710602,-0.042999268,-0.017608643,-0.043395996,0.036895752,-0.027633667,-0.05480957,0.007949829,0.004699707,0.010749817,0.015808105,-0.004386902,-0.010322571,0.032287598,-0.053375244,-0.057556152,0.027297974,-0.013023376,0.059448242,0.0071525574,-0.035186768,-0.016342163,0.03918457,0.07897949,-0.00365448,0.018615723,-0.034729004,0.034362793,-0.006385803,0.019805908,0.04977417,0.010810852,0.029541016,0.0256958,-0.024993896,0.023345947,-0.022094727,0.02848816,-0.011154175,-0.03540039,0.041900635,0.021209717,-0.0027656555,-0.013031006,-0.0018033981,0.009529114,0.024780273,-0.0038700104,-0.019378662,-0.008132935,-0.029022217,-0.037353516,-0.017959595,0.018661499,-0.016082764,-0.027923584,-0.06512451,-0.04824829,-0.055480957,-0.0033035278,-0.05380249,0.0028896332,-0.022094727,0.0022602081,-0.004562378,-0.014602661,0.013412476,-0.022064209,0.007865906,0.036132812,0.016723633,-0.028747559,0.0057792664,-0.020263672,0.01007843,-0.0022392273,0.04901123,0.029067993,0.020339966,-0.038146973,0.04849243,0.013977051,0.0003812313,0.041778564,0.035064697,-0.03591919,-0.028259277,-0.030273438,0.019592285,-0.029708862,-0.033477783,-0.020935059,0.0037822723,-0.012016296,-0.008033752,-0.04928589,0.027877808,0.010467529,-0.0362854,-0.015563965,0.017654419,0.0256958,0.05142212,-0.029663086,-0.0069351196,-0.0004901886,0.016708374,0.002943039,-0.049438477,-0.010467529,0.016021729,0.02368164,0.010810852,0.021484375,-0.05429077,-0.025421143,0.016418457,0.036468506,0.022872925,0.036254883,-0.013328552,-0.004852295,-0.024993896,0.029800415,0.023712158,-0.01499176,0.0138168335,0.00035619736,0.000349