(2212,	NULL,	NULL,	'## 3.3 Articulación institucional y proyección

Esta ruta no solo responde al marco DigComp, sino que se alinea integralmente con el PEI de la UNAB, el cual plantea como prioridad el desarrollo de competencias tecnológicas, el pensamiento crítico, la responsabilidad ética, la innovación, la sostenibilidad y la acción ciudadana.
Asimismo, la ruta se conecta con:
El componente sociohumanístico reformado, especialmente en los desafíos sobre el desarrollo tecnológico, la democracia, la equidad social y la sostenibilidad ambiental.
Los ciclos formativos (común, mayor y menor), facilitando la incorporación progresiva y estratégica de estas competencias en todos los niveles curriculares.
La formación en ciudadanía digital, eje transversal de la educación del siglo XXI.
Los propósitos de empleabilidad e internacionalización, al proporcionar herramientas que permiten a los egresados competir y adaptarse a entornos globales.

## 3.4. En resumen, el nuevo ciclo formativo',	'[0.0059051514,0.017196655,0.05014038,0.026992798,0.01663208,0.022003174,0.045715332,0.051940918,-0.027664185,0.032806396,0.0234375,-0.04043579,-0.016983032,-0.03274536,-0.009384155,0.010360718,-0.042816162,-0.034240723,0.03491211,0.06100464,0.04034424,-0.02949524,-0.005176544,0.027435303,-0.018676758,-0.020996094,0.03378296,0.03881836,-0.03704834,0.019638062,0.0184021,-0.044006348,-0.005016327,-0.012763977,-0.019073486,-0.014228821,-0.052581787,0.07110596,0.0058517456,0.007904053,0.035461426,0.015930176,-0.008094788,-0.02722168,-0.06951904,-0.027999878,-0.026504517,0.012489319,0.034240723,0.065979004,-0.028060913,0.02557373,0.10461426,0.044555664,-0.03604126,0.014533997,-0.013542175,-0.032226562,-0.007369995,-0.0112838745,0.043640137,-0.0034599304,0.038848877,0.02041626,0.011543274,0.012962341,-0.012954712,0.026824951,-0.02557373,-0.03765869,0.0038070679,0.010520935,-0.0033073425,-0.025619507,-0.018722534,-0.004886627,-0.007511139,-0.018981934,-0.027862549,-0.037902832,-0.035461426,-0.026229858,0.020004272,-0.029220581,0.001045227,-0.03427124,-0.066345215,-0.049041748,-0.027755737,0.016571045,-0.032043457,-0.029724121,-0.036987305,0.05014038,0.017700195,0.0209198,0.006729126,-0.03326416,0.0129852295,0.020263672,0.024795532,-0.041290283,-0.0062026978,-0.01864624,0.018737793,-0.019882202,-0.02180481,-0.009017944,-0.0059318542,-0.016235352,0.0016918182,0.019561768,0.033996582,0.06933594,0.05303955,-0.056121826,-0.008262634,-0.028686523,-0.0058631897,-0.011268616,0.007160187,-0.036895752,-0.018615723,0.009117126,0.010910034,-0.05230713,0.023529053,0.012634277,-0.053833008,-0.052368164,-0.027297974,-0.004627228,0.012275696,-0.018630981,-0.01600647,-0.014556885,-0.017196655,-0.022460938,-0.0124435425,-0.027114868,0.029296875,-0.026504517,-0.012184143,0.017791748,-0.02330017,0.02418518,0.0015001297,0.037628174,0.040222168,0.044921875,-0.04348755,0.013839722,-0.04714966,0.019607544,0.001709938,-0.015602112,-0.057281494,-0.0153