(2213,	NULL,	NULL,	'## 3.4. En resumen, el nuevo ciclo formativo

La ruta de formación en Competencias Digitales para el aprendizaje y el trabajo no es un componente aislado ni instrumental. Es una estrategia educativa integral que potencia el desarrollo de una ciudadanía crítica, creativa, colaborativa y transformadora, al tiempo que fortalece el perfil profesional de los estudiantes UNAB.
Esta propuesta no solo actualiza tecnológicamente el currículo, sino que refuerza la misión institucional de formar personas éticas, comprometidas con su entorno y preparadas para liderar en la sociedad digital.

# Propuesta de operación de la Ruta de Formación en Competencias Digitales para el Aprendizaje y el Trabajo',	'[0.011390686,0.040863037,0.004550934,0.016113281,0.03338623,-0.019210815,0.06451416,0.067871094,0.0034008026,0.036743164,0.017608643,-0.03137207,-0.016998291,-0.038085938,0.008026123,0.0284729,-0.023284912,-0.02935791,0.010314941,0.061676025,0.038757324,-0.046020508,0.008995056,-0.0016841888,-0.008071899,-0.030288696,0.01108551,0.027664185,-0.058532715,0.0017461777,-0.013549805,-0.036254883,-0.02798462,-0.007820129,0.027267456,0.0022277832,-0.011054993,0.05883789,0.022537231,-0.005794525,0.02999878,-0.006641388,0.019195557,0.004070282,-0.048034668,-0.009925842,-0.0023441315,0.024642944,0.023590088,0.04714966,-0.022338867,0.03390503,0.078308105,0.038635254,-0.044525146,0.0036506653,-0.02394104,-0.057800293,-0.024993896,0.014213562,0.040039062,0.008003235,0.022201538,0.0335083,0.016448975,0.01586914,-0.026611328,0.034057617,-0.022842407,-0.03186035,0.01914978,-0.00040555,0.014968872,-0.012702942,-0.013519287,0.004547119,0.002729416,-0.028320312,-0.023269653,-0.0049743652,-0.022323608,-0.010383606,0.042297363,-0.02130127,-0.017303467,-0.010627747,-0.067993164,-0.0647583,0.007572174,-0.0071029663,-0.024597168,-0.0137786865,-0.040496826,0.059051514,0.021484375,0.01184845,-0.0084991455,-0.0115737915,0.019683838,0.01876831,0.021102905,-0.040924072,0.004016876,-0.0039634705,0.003490448,-0.030151367,-0.015098572,-0.011871338,-0.010368347,-0.004047394,-0.027923584,0.0067977905,0.038970947,0.013763428,0.059173584,-0.07879639,0.0020103455,-0.028778076,-0.008529663,-0.008781433,0.0026798248,-0.03805542,-0.039794922,-0.0046195984,-0.019744873,-0.045135498,0.04031372,0.035064697,-0.06365967,-0.0625,-0.0231781,-0.022262573,-0.0025463104,-0.026611328,-0.011505127,-0.022125244,-0.03302002,-0.00187397,-0.03704834,-0.025100708,-0.0019302368,-0.023422241,-0.013122559,0.018478394,-0.042388916,-0.00598526,0.030349731,0.072387695,0.044403076,0.036102295,-0.040496826,0.007499695,-0