(2218,	NULL,	NULL,	'## 4.4. Reconocimiento: Insignia de Competencias Digitales

Los estudiantes que completen satisfactoriamente los tres cursos de la ruta (uno por cada pilar) ya sea que lo realizó en la oferta de cursos de la UNAB , o reconocidos a través de la prueba diagnóstica de competencias o certificaciones digitales, recibirán una Insignia Digital UNAB con el título “Competencias Digitales”.
Ventajas de la Insignia para la empleabilidad:
Validación de habilidades digitales transversales reconocidas por estándares internacionales como DigComp.
Evidencia de formación complementaria aplicable a contextos laborales, de emprendimiento y académicos.
Potencial para ser incluida en hojas de vida, portafolios digitales, redes profesionales (LinkedIn) y plataformas de microcredenciales.
Diferenciación en procesos de selección y prácticas profesionales al demostrar dominio en tecnologías emergentes, productividad digital, ética tecnológica y comunicación estratégica.',	'[0.035949707,0.023010254,0.027297974,0.03729248,-0.006996155,-0.013954163,0.014389038,0.042297363,0.0050811768,0.01713562,0.038513184,-0.018997192,-0.011177063,-0.074645996,0.022567749,0.057037354,-0.05783081,-0.028366089,-0.014137268,0.08312988,0.046417236,-0.023071289,0.026794434,0.029144287,0.0385437,-0.007549286,0.013877869,0.02154541,-0.015853882,-0.011642456,0.005268097,-0.03375244,-0.01474762,-0.027008057,0.016983032,0.044403076,0.003376007,0.062927246,-0.006793976,-0.020584106,-0.00072431564,0.0340271,0.0012655258,-0.039001465,-0.059783936,-0.006629944,-0.024276733,-0.018325806,0.01826477,0.048583984,-0.037994385,0.032440186,0.04714966,0.049346924,-0.059661865,-0.016799927,-0.0055160522,-0.031799316,-0.0055274963,-0.030578613,0.007369995,0.032287598,0.044036865,0.046447754,0.022918701,0.015731812,-0.049194336,0.041870117,-0.017333984,-0.021392822,0.035125732,-0.0023994446,-0.0028820038,0.0049209595,-0.025039673,0.041748047,0.009063721,0.011566162,-0.009925842,-0.033081055,-0.03390503,-0.008712769,0.026443481,-0.046844482,-0.0015554428,0.008003235,-0.046447754,-0.08618164,-0.029281616,0.03074646,-0.014671326,0.0054397583,-0.019073486,0.030029297,0.011001587,0.028839111,0.006916046,-0.013206482,-0.0073623657,0.043701172,-0.0002374649,-0.00970459,0.022369385,-0.024291992,0.011917114,-0.0036792755,0.0010766983,-0.0043144226,0.010467529,0.02217102,-0.005355835,0.046569824,0.01133728,0.03829956,0.05117798,-0.07598877,-0.03173828,-0.09631348,0.0018014908,-0.027023315,-0.021942139,-0.033447266,-0.02619934,-0.02961731,-0.029937744,-0.049194336,0.015899658,0.023284912,-0.030532837,-0.059783936,-0.047424316,0.012954712,0.004348755,-0.03982544,-0.0013914108,-0.005607605,-0.014007568,-0.058776855,-0.046173096,-0.0035476685,-0.014717102,-0.021453857,0.0038261414,0.003238678,-0.05267334,-0.