(2220,	NULL,	NULL,	'## 4.6. Adaptación para programas T&T y modalidad Dual

Dado que los programas de Técnica y Tecnología (T&T) y los de modalidad Dual manejan estructuras curriculares distintas:
Se diseñará un plan de equivalencias que permita reconocer y ajustar la ruta de competencias digitales conforme a su normativa.
En estos casos, los cursos sí podrán otorgar créditos académicos, por lo cual deberán alinearse a las Normas de Competencia Laboral del Ministerio de Trabajo y al modelo pedagógico de formación DUAL.
La Dirección de Competencias Digitales (DCD) acompañará estos procesos, ajustando los contenidos y metodologías e informar en debida forma ante el MEN la modificación, antes de poder implementarla, por lo cual se debe establecer claramente cuál es el plan de transición para estos programas: equivalencias..
El plan de transición para Dual está en estudio por parte del área correspondiente, dado que se soporta en requerimientos del modelo Alemán. La propuesta de equivalencias es:',	'[-0.0025100708,0.04458618,0.060058594,0.0004720688,0.017654419,0.03857422,0.032165527,0.044006348,-0.01776123,0.014007568,0.03050232,-0.026123047,-0.00047564507,-0.021438599,-0.02267456,0.045532227,0.0075645447,-0.028717041,0.024658203,0.06524658,0.00029969215,-0.013694763,0.021774292,0.030960083,0.07080078,-0.0546875,0.023101807,0.010543823,-4.351139e-06,-0.023117065,0.015975952,-0.03050232,-0.01966858,-0.010597229,0.04812622,-0.0025310516,-0.015296936,0.10479736,0.031982422,0.0021877289,-0.026275635,0.027145386,-0.03756714,0.021911621,-0.0657959,-0.0048828125,-0.014419556,0.0020923615,0.010093689,0.03729248,0.026504517,0.0037899017,0.026275635,0.060760498,-0.028381348,0.020584106,-0.020095825,-0.002626419,-0.015174866,-0.031799316,0.023468018,0.0008907318,0.04095459,0.014541626,0.0012874603,0.00013005733,-0.061828613,-0.00013184547,-0.030792236,0.007926941,-0.020370483,0.03265381,0.015213013,-0.016555786,-0.026443481,0.053497314,-0.0011034012,0.019180298,0.0026397705,0.014274597,-0.026412964,0.0038146973,0.007888794,-0.022033691,0.0107803345,0.019195557,-0.049743652,-0.036834717,-0.009353638,-0.03643799,-0.011428833,0.0019874573,-0.050842285,0.046020508,0.02607727,0.0010051727,-0.027160645,-0.010604858,-0.0010681152,0.029434204,0.03289795,-0.020751953,0.027526855,-0.006126404,0.040802002,-0.015068054,-0.023712158,0.015808105,-0.048736572,-0.0016145706,0.03286743,0.023483276,0.037597656,-0.0058517456,0.05102539,-0.07385254,0.014213562,-0.021316528,-0.0022583008,-0.02583313,-0.04626465,-0.01423645,-0.026565552,-0.016983032,-0.0016326904,-0.02746582,0.007472992,0.019210815,-0.057250977,-0.0340271,-0.035949707,-0.014945984,-0.031402588,-0.01852417,-0.02760315,-0.013076782,-0.050598145,-0.018753052,-0.0065727234,-0.030395508,0.017730713,-0.004524231,-0.0005106926,0.03704834,-0.05331421,0.028121