(2222,	NULL,	NULL,	'## 4.7. Coordinación académica y planificación institucional

La programación de los cursos se realizará de forma articulada con la oferta institucional bajo el esquema PG (períodos globales), en coordinación directa con las direcciones de programa, tal como se realiza actualmente con otros departamentos transversales como:
Departamento de Lenguas
Departamento de estudios Sociohumanísticos
Departamento de Ciencias Básicas
Además, el Departamento de Competencias Digitales apoyará a los programas que requieran reportes al Ministerio de Educación Nacional, incluyendo:
Alineación con estándares internacionales
Ajustes curriculares
Inclusión en informes de autoevaluación o registros calificados

## 4.8. Oferta dinámica y evolución permanente de la ruta',	'[-0.035491943,0.026031494,0.08404541,-0.0035953522,-0.026977539,0.029556274,0.029220581,0.031677246,-0.012016296,-0.0018482208,0.024642944,-0.029968262,0.0070152283,-0.042755127,-0.024993896,0.030258179,-0.033813477,-0.0018596649,0.011009216,0.0524292,0.021636963,-0.04916382,0.0041160583,0.02128601,0.017089844,-0.038970947,0.021453857,0.06866455,-0.01751709,-0.002626419,0.04663086,-0.025421143,-0.0061912537,-0.022369385,-0.02166748,-0.0056152344,-0.011238098,0.05404663,0.01701355,-0.018478394,0.010284424,0.0051116943,-0.03338623,0.016601562,-0.042907715,0.009277344,-0.041900635,0.022583008,0.03375244,0.028244019,-0.033111572,0.015319824,0.05319214,0.033691406,-0.0016746521,0.021392822,0.024368286,-0.03164673,-0.014007568,-0.014656067,0.042388916,-0.030075073,0.03225708,0.024719238,0.023605347,0.01612854,-0.053222656,-0.0022144318,-0.011367798,-0.02734375,0.011070251,0.01939392,0.018173218,-0.026000977,0.0066833496,0.044311523,-0.0065727234,-0.010269165,-0.019866943,-0.005290985,-0.009017944,0.017700195,0.047943115,-0.030044556,-0.01574707,-0.029281616,-0.05810547,0.0018396378,-0.030960083,-0.010391235,-0.018478394,0.012664795,-0.060058594,0.04736328,0.022567749,-0.013183594,-0.004272461,-0.030456543,0.023040771,0.039001465,0.043670654,-0.052459717,-0.023895264,-0.025344849,0.03488159,0.0045433044,-0.022994995,0.03189087,-0.07720947,-0.025512695,-0.0059509277,-0.007972717,0.025802612,-0.007881165,0.036132812,-0.06817627,0.0074157715,-0.005355835,-0.028167725,-0.020935059,-0.021774292,-0.03567505,0.0046844482,0.010017395,-0.00058460236,-0.029708862,-0.0068511963,-0.021087646,-0.064697266,-0.038360596,-0.04272461,-0.022842407,-0.01701355,-0.023422241,-0.026290894,0.0046691895,-0.015342712,-0.03326416,0.0045318604,-0.007259369,0.06359863,0.039031982,-0.052734375,0.04824829,-0.013374329,0.03286743,0.011398315,0.02670288,0.032470703,0.007865906,-0.0016870499,0.008644104,-0.031951904,-0.021881104,0.010971069,0.00