(2223,	NULL,	NULL,	'La operación de esta ruta no solo responde a las necesidades actuales de transformación digital, sino que configura un modelo educativo innovador, dinámico y sostenible. Contribuye a la formación integral del estudiante UNAB, mejora su perfil de egreso, fortalece su empleabilidad y permite al mismo tiempo cumplir con estándares internacionales de calidad educativa en la era digital.
Uno de los principios fundamentales de la Ruta de Formación en Competencias Digitales es su capacidad de adaptación continua frente al vertiginoso avance tecnológico, la transformación del mercado laboral y las nuevas necesidades formativas identificadas por los programas académicos.
Por esta razón, la oferta de cursos dentro de la ruta se concibe como dinámica y en permanente evolución, lo que implica:
Actualización periódica de contenidos de los cursos existentes, integrando nuevas herramientas, tecnologías emergentes, marcos normativos actualizados, y tendencias pedagógicas.',	'[-0.0048065186,0.027526855,0.05102539,0.021774292,0.011054993,-0.024734497,0.056549072,0.09692383,-0.008483887,0.02696228,0.021057129,-0.027862549,-0.032073975,-0.04837036,0.0023117065,0.017745972,-0.014762878,-0.044036865,-0.00818634,0.049194336,0.035614014,-0.07354736,0.0028133392,0.0008049011,-0.008384705,-0.03665161,-0.0060653687,0.034454346,-0.04638672,-0.026428223,0.0017213821,-0.02470398,-0.02319336,-0.019134521,0.012069702,0.015487671,-0.0036907196,0.05267334,0.026641846,-0.007789612,0.018722534,0.009841919,0.004508972,-0.020111084,-0.05319214,-0.009475708,-0.0049438477,-0.01626587,0.031402588,0.03640747,-0.056732178,0.013252258,0.051849365,0.032348633,-0.02885437,0.004085541,0.0051574707,-0.0362854,0.010070801,0.0015029907,0.042236328,-0.01436615,0.011077881,0.01626587,0.014289856,0.030776978,-0.043701172,0.029510498,-0.062683105,-0.029373169,0.017074585,-0.0289917,0.017913818,-0.02722168,-0.017288208,0.022033691,0.012718201,0.0284729,-0.016998291,-0.019714355,-0.012916565,-0.012145996,0.04046631,-0.04360962,-0.0051841736,0.015449524,-0.044647217,-0.07244873,-0.03363037,0.006477356,-0.014968872,0.011413574,-0.028121948,0.041290283,-0.005619049,0.0132751465,0.01146698,-0.010360718,0.030426025,0.025360107,0.04522705,-0.04815674,0.019989014,-0.016616821,-0.011100769,-0.034179688,-0.015045166,-0.012016296,-0.01852417,0.0003414154,0.0024776459,-0.03137207,0.05529785,-0.0073013306,0.06274414,-0.05783081,0.010353088,-0.027999878,-0.02041626,0.0019607544,-0.003967285,-0.04626465,-0.03756714,-0.00039219856,-0.009971619,-0.066101074,0.016036987,0.038330078,-0.030944824,-0.05331421,-0.033721924,-0.006084442,-0.0007071495,-0.019058228,-0.02482605,-0.013168335,-0.041778564,-0.010902405,-0.0010690689,-0.0024375916,-0.0011730194,-0.0032997131,-0.029769897,0.04336548,-0.062927246,0.0023231506,0.