(2224,	NULL,	NULL,	'Actualización periódica de contenidos de los cursos existentes, integrando nuevas herramientas, tecnologías emergentes, marcos normativos actualizados, y tendencias pedagógicas.
Inclusión de nuevos cursos dentro de los pilares establecidos, que respondan a:
Innovaciones tecnológicas disruptivas (como nuevas aplicaciones de IA, blockchain, realidad extendida, etc.)
Requerimientos específicos de formación detectados por programas académicos o sectores productivos
Demandas de los propios estudiantes en procesos participativos de mejora continua
Flexibilidad curricular para reorganizar, renombrar o sustituir cursos dentro de cada pilar, garantizando la pertinencia y alineación con los objetivos del modelo educativo institucional y con marcos de referencia internacionales como el Marco Europeo de Competencia Digital (DigComp), la UNESCO, la OEA, o el Foro Económico Mundial.',	'[-0.016677856,0.054870605,0.067993164,-0.0043678284,-0.0013780594,0.028411865,0.050323486,0.04119873,-0.006969452,0.04248047,0.06188965,-0.010185242,-0.017089844,-0.007041931,-0.00623703,0.047454834,-0.00033426285,-0.022872925,0.0126571655,0.029296875,0.00019228458,-0.045074463,0.0063591003,0.043884277,0.010856628,-0.007797241,0.037231445,0.051696777,-0.013191223,-0.021881104,0.05670166,-0.02218628,-0.042785645,0.0047912598,-0.004299164,-0.015991211,-0.03353882,0.061279297,0.032592773,0.0061950684,0.010879517,-0.004261017,-0.014282227,0.0001693964,-0.051696777,-0.03277588,-0.026397705,-0.028915405,0.027938843,0.070373535,-0.010559082,0.004547119,0.047454834,-0.0047569275,0.0017299652,-0.0078086853,-0.008888245,0.010017395,-0.0007491112,0.024032593,0.04220581,0.0018949509,0.038330078,0.012039185,-0.004573822,0.0030670166,-0.04248047,0.007637024,-0.030670166,0.0026817322,-0.019470215,0.0074310303,-0.026687622,0.00026893616,-0.00015771389,0.014678955,0.038391113,-0.0015277863,-0.039154053,-0.0030994415,0.019012451,0.011383057,0.01928711,-0.048309326,-0.0048065186,0.000521183,-0.06628418,0.00579834,-0.033294678,-0.025665283,-0.053833008,-0.004501343,-0.05206299,0.020904541,-0.023117065,-0.003774643,0.015853882,-0.02696228,0.01826477,0.033721924,0.044799805,-0.0690918,0.0029563904,-0.039398193,0.022399902,-0.032043457,-0.0004811287,-0.008468628,-0.05206299,0.0009784698,-0.008888245,-0.029312134,-0.005695343,-0.030059814,0.02041626,-0.0803833,-0.008018494,-0.0065841675,-0.04434204,-0.004940033,-0.024261475,-0.035369873,-0.049224854,0.012611389,-0.009170532,-0.0647583,0.015235901,0.010803223,-0.029846191,-0.061065674,-0.041778564,0.0032997131