(2225,	NULL,	NULL,	'Adicionalmente, esta oferta dinámica será acompañada por un proceso sistemático de evaluación y retroalimentación, en el cual se integrarán:
Resultados de encuestas a estudiantes, egresados y docentes
Indicadores de desempeño en los cursos
Reportes de tendencias globales en educación digital y tecnología educativa
Observaciones de comités curriculares y académicos de los programas
Gracias a esta estrategia de mejora continua, la ruta no se limita a un conjunto fijo de contenidos, sino que se proyecta como un ecosistema de formación digital adaptable, que permite a la UNAB responder con agilidad a los cambios tecnológicos, garantizar la vigencia del aprendizaje, y reforzar el compromiso institucional con una educación moderna, pertinente y orientada al futuro.',	'[0.0076789856,0.027023315,0.032409668,0.021743774,0.0005559921,0.01637268,0.027954102,0.066711426,0.005203247,0.04623413,0.03353882,-0.04776001,-0.013160706,-0.041503906,0.0007276535,0.044036865,-0.024505615,-0.017410278,0.008033752,0.03704834,0.011642456,-0.05987549,0.019042969,0.01576233,0.007713318,-0.059570312,-0.0071258545,0.037994385,-0.025161743,-0.012771606,0.028015137,-0.030944824,-0.009750366,-0.0018863678,-0.0052452087,0.027175903,-0.023483276,0.04949951,0.024368286,-0.03643799,0.00042057037,0.003168106,0.017166138,-0.006412506,-0.04812622,-0.022583008,-0.04510498,-0.032470703,0.022323608,0.0446167,-0.05795288,0.029174805,0.03363037,-0.013969421,-0.012031555,-0.007789612,0.0015039444,-0.0031814575,-0.016326904,0.0069770813,0.03765869,0.0010929108,0.04437256,0.022613525,0.020217896,0.0015592575,-0.03466797,0.038604736,-0.052001953,-0.016281128,0.03894043,-0.015640259,-0.011665344,-0.012321472,-0.024642944,0.021713257,0.04196167,0.0045433044,-0.009086609,-0.013191223,0.0104904175,0.0071754456,0.030075073,-0.04220581,-0.007095337,0.0118637085,-0.054901123,-0.044006348,-0.03555298,0.0057907104,-0.024398804,0.030654907,-0.04586792,0.07171631,-0.0008778572,0.029937744,0.0036468506,-0.049713135,0.023529053,-0.0016460419,0.032470703,-0.056427002,-0.0029888153,-0.011642456,0.022644043,-0.026763916,-0.0289917,-0.01499176,-0.017822266,-0.0017681122,0.026824951,-0.028503418,0.030151367,0.002817154,0.039886475,-0.056365967,0.0044937134,-0.016860962,-0.030715942,-0.013465881,-0.029083252,-0.032165527,0.0021209717,-0.0040016174,-0.010307312,-0.06793213,0.012382507,-0.009567261,-0.05932617