(2227,	NULL,	NULL,	'Este proceso se considera un cambio no estructural, conforme al Decreto 0529 de 2024, lo que permite su implementación sin requerir autorización previa del Ministerio de Educación Nacional. se mantendrá el respeto por la estructura de los planes de estudio actuales, sin modificar el número de créditos ni alterar las competencias formativas generales definidas en el PEI.
Estudiantes antiguos y estudiantes nuevos
Estudiantes antiguos (ingreso antes del periodo 202560)
Los estudiantes que hayan iniciado su carrera antes del segundo semestre de 2025 (202560), contarán con un periodo de transición de un semestre adicional (hasta el final del 202560) para completar los cursos del plan anterior ofertados por el Departamento de Informática. Es decir, se garantizará la oferta completa de los cursos de Cultura Informática durante este periodo para que puedan culminar sus obligaciones académicas sin afectaciones.',	'[0.006187439,0.011474609,0.02494812,-0.013153076,-0.008384705,0.009292603,0.018478394,0.05316162,-0.01663208,-0.028930664,0.06085205,-0.0054359436,-0.008369446,0.004306793,-0.01776123,0.016906738,-0.031951904,-0.01448822,-0.008926392,0.02470398,0.010917664,-0.025482178,-0.013534546,0.00048398972,0.0037994385,-0.030166626,-0.013053894,0.038360596,-0.008079529,-0.0048980713,0.050842285,-0.022201538,-0.023651123,-0.021133423,-0.0051651,-0.013786316,-0.047027588,0.029785156,0.022460938,-0.045715332,0.012962341,0.024520874,-0.03793335,-0.0058784485,-0.04248047,0.014945984,0.003780365,-0.0013742447,0.04598999,0.07678223,-0.009811401,-0.012268066,0.013496399,0.035705566,-0.014335632,-0.002735138,0.023651123,-0.00026202202,-0.036315918,-0.018081665,0.06964111,0.020950317,0.050964355,0.0044441223,0.010391235,0.015151978,-0.030792236,0.050933838,-0.022598267,-0.012283325,-0.051757812,0.024612427,-0.013809204,-0.044036865,-0.041992188,0.07763672,0.0067710876,0.024719238,0.024719238,-0.009269714,-0.013877869,0.013656616,0.019882202,-0.009170532,-0.004058838,0.0647583,-0.050354004,-0.015533447,0.007801056,-0.032958984,-0.012741089,-0.010498047,-0.06732178,0.010047913,-0.0027503967,-0.004119873,-0.014541626,-0.06390381,0.01914978,0.054229736,-0.0049972534,-0.036254883,0.009147644,-0.021240234,0.017410278,-0.024475098,-0.009307861,0.019927979,-0.05444336,-0.040496826,0.032196045,0.002029419,0.06298828,0.0062332153,0.03414917,-0.064819336,-0.007713318,-0.036956787,0.00032424927,-0.007850647,-0.022155762,-0.024932861,-0.0138549805,-0.013626099