(2230,	NULL,	NULL,	'Para los estudiantes que ingresen a partir del periodo 202560, se inicia la implementación del nuevo modelo de formación con el curso obligatorio Interacción Digital, primer componente de la ruta de Competencias Digitales. No obstante, debido a las adecuaciones requeridas en los sistemas financieros y de matrícula de la Universidad, estos estudiantes no serán prematriculados ni verán reflejado el valor del curso en su recibo de matrícula para ese primer semestre.
Por esta razón, durante el 202560, los estudiantes nuevos tendrán las siguientes alternativas:
Presentar la prueba de diagnóstico de Competencias Digitales, la cual se aplicará durante la semana de inducción y evaluará conocimientos alineados al curso “Interacción Digital”, incluyendo resolución de problemas, creación de presentaciones, hojas de cálculo y herramientas web. Dependiendo de la modalidad de estudio será presencial o virtual.',	'[-0.0385437,0.035308838,0.03930664,0.010871887,-0.018936157,0.010414124,0.043060303,0.046142578,0.001332283,0.019500732,0.0039405823,-0.024124146,0.00045371056,-0.045898438,-0.0058784485,0.043426514,-0.041168213,-0.018753052,-0.043548584,0.08300781,0.053619385,-0.019546509,0.0049552917,-0.0056915283,0.0012865067,-0.019348145,-0.0065193176,0.0018386841,-0.021697998,-0.0019044876,0.0154800415,-0.034454346,-0.03616333,-0.0036392212,-0.03491211,0.012191772,-0.04562378,0.076293945,-0.00021219254,-0.016708374,-0.026809692,0.059509277,-0.014167786,-0.021347046,-0.05102539,0.018112183,0.010108948,-0.06036377,0.048919678,0.029464722,-0.046844482,0.0031719208,0.04067993,0.037506104,-0.042999268,-0.008430481,-0.0021743774,-0.012245178,-0.019134521,0.0048942566,0.05407715,0.009681702,0.010482788,0.006378174,0.039520264,0.001912117,-0.0390625,0.059631348,-0.0037765503,-0.0096588135,-0.053710938,-0.005844116,0.015266418,-0.00447464,-0.03250122,0.056243896,-0.00554657,-0.024154663,0.0044403076,-0.016677856,-0.014656067,0.0012578964,-0.00021529198,-0.019607544,0.0033302307,0.06201172,-0.053222656,-0.026550293,0.0023994446,-0.027328491,-0.002243042,0.009239197,-0.06982422,0.06768799,-0.008049011,0.0022068024,-0.026901245,-0.05380249,0.024047852,0.02748108,0.018173218,-0.021240234,0.020507812,0.00019419193,0.014762878,-0.035247803,-0.0014438629,0.018814087,-0.017349243,0.019012451,0.05960083,0.01939392,0.021438599,-0.0030612946,0.060546875,-0.039916992,-0.023468018,-0.05255127,-0.051239014,-0.055236816,0.007858276,-0.005367279,-0.024841309,-0.02520752,-0.028900146,-0.06384277,0.0129470825,0.017166138,-0.07513428,-0.05697632,-0.019500732,-0.