(2235,	NULL,	NULL,	'## 6.1. Condición especial para programas profesionales virtuales

Para los programas de formación profesional en modalidad virtual, la ruta de competencias digitales iniciará a partir del segundo semestre académico de formación, lo cual permite que los estudiantes puedan acceder a los cursos una vez estén disponibles en formato 100% virtual. Por tanto, los estudiantes virtuales que ingresen en el 202560 no tomarán el curso Interacción Digital en ese semestre, ya que aún no estará virtualizado.

## 6.2. Fases del Plan de Virtualización

El plan está organizado en tres fases distribuidas entre los semestres 202560 y 202620, asegurando que para el año 2027 la oferta esté completamente implementada para programas virtuales.

#### Fase 1 – Segundo semestre de 2025 (202560)',	'[-0.031280518,0.03817749,0.060455322,-0.018157959,-0.0064430237,0.015899658,0.006969452,0.039001465,0.0026855469,0.0082473755,0.019866943,-0.014137268,-0.022949219,-0.04650879,-0.017623901,0.042877197,-0.034057617,0.018859863,-0.006000519,0.019683838,0.06088257,-0.039031982,-0.0051002502,0.0013885498,-0.009025574,-0.037231445,0.03579712,0.057250977,-0.016479492,0.005264282,0.02456665,-0.041748047,-0.006515503,-0.04824829,0.0053901672,-0.00018548965,-0.044403076,0.06390381,-0.0034160614,0.002216339,-0.005329132,0.019500732,-0.024719238,0.032348633,-0.03112793,0.022979736,0.016296387,-0.029251099,0.03741455,0.06036377,-0.008995056,-0.014053345,0.029342651,0.06628418,-0.050354004,-0.026794434,0.0047302246,-0.009506226,-0.022033691,-0.035125732,0.04562378,0.018295288,0.022750854,0.04309082,0.026535034,0.018112183,-0.023010254,0.03744507,-0.02558899,-0.012535095,-0.035980225,0.043273926,0.006401062,-0.0058898926,-0.038208008,0.06008911,-0.014595032,-0.006580353,0.010063171,-0.02645874,-0.018692017,0.03869629,0.015853882,-0.0059394836,0.008262634,0.016433716,-0.05050659,-0.018966675,0.0011014938,0.0006713867,-0.015106201,0.025634766,-0.08123779,0.04901123,0.035461426,0.039794922,-0.0005059242,-0.034118652,-0.0023593903,0.025253296,-0.0020179749,-0.035003662,0.005558014,-0.012069702,0.021530151,-0.017700195,0.0040626526,0.041870117,-0.027755737,-0.026016235,0.04638672,0.02178955,0.050323486,-0.006378174,0.02128601,-0.046722412,0.013031006,-0.06604004,-0.02796936,-0.02418518,-0.008369446,0.016326904,-0.03353882,-0.033477783,-0.009765625,-0.033050537,0.0018234253,0.02658081,-0.056030273,-0.045440674,-0.0592041,-0.015792847,-0.006008148,-0.050354004,-0.0234375,-0.011497498,-0.02468872,0.006919861,-0.015701294,-0.034179688,-0.012626648,-0.024032593,0.017501831,0.0026569366,-0.024993896,-0.002380371,-0.0020198822,0.025436401,0.0049552917,0.018798828,-0.04058838,-0.03665161,0.01109314,-0.02116394,0.022705078,0.005027771,-0.05560