(2239,	NULL,	NULL,	'Conoce y aplica las funcionalidades de las herramientas o aplicaciones más comunes de los programas y cierra brechas digitales.
La transformación de la formación en competencias digitales reconoce que no todos los estudiantes ingresan con el mismo nivel de apropiación tecnológica, debido a contextos desiguales en su formación previa. Por tanto, la Oferta de Cursos Bajo Demanda surge como una estrategia complementaria para:
Atender brechas digitales específicas detectadas en estudiantes provenientes de instituciones educativas con baja o nula formación en herramientas informáticas.
Responder a necesidades particulares de los programas académicos, en casos donde se requieren habilidades en herramientas o aplicaciones digitales que no están cubiertas por la ruta formal de competencias digitales.',	'[-0.01626587,0.042816162,0.04232788,0.004261017,0.041534424,-0.04284668,0.041503906,0.093566895,-0.012870789,0.04397583,0.022766113,-0.019805908,-0.00472641,-0.04348755,0.009246826,0.020065308,0.012619019,-0.03955078,0.011390686,0.06500244,0.036132812,-0.022094727,-0.023406982,0.01914978,0.016921997,-0.034362793,-0.0047340393,0.017684937,-0.043792725,0.019943237,0.015808105,-0.018615723,-0.06732178,-0.017852783,0.08673096,0.04083252,-0.029418945,0.0657959,0.023345947,0.02607727,-0.011016846,0.01725769,-0.030975342,-0.0040359497,-0.053985596,-0.0013751984,-0.014205933,-0.051818848,0.008865356,0.052764893,-0.028701782,0.008026123,0.04348755,0.04473877,-0.012359619,0.0047073364,-0.04159546,-0.009521484,-0.005382538,0.01486969,0.044311523,-0.0048332214,0.03250122,0.054260254,0.006099701,0.056549072,-0.039733887,6.592274e-05,-0.044830322,0.012489319,0.013748169,-0.009902954,-0.0067367554,-0.0076560974,0.0004644394,0.046691895,0.019851685,0.025772095,-0.0064430237,0.013420105,0.031036377,-0.03173828,0.009353638,-0.047973633,-0.03286743,0.015022278,-0.036987305,-0.023605347,-0.033050537,-0.021636963,-0.025436401,0.013244629,-0.02659607,0.035705566,-0.026870728,0.03604126,-0.0047683716,-0.001449585,0.017364502,0.062927246,0.023406982,-0.0005197525,0.019866943,-0.050445557,0.027801514,-0.035003662,-0.018997192,-0.03829956,-0.022705078,0.02067566,0.00032401085,-0.027526855,0.031082153,0.009178162,0.04257202,-0.035125732,-0.009765625,-0.035125732,0.010803223,0.007205963,-0.03060913,-0.02822876,-0.05517578,0.018829346,-0.014228821,-0.04711914,0.010757446,0.012908936,-0.018203735,-0.05883789,-0.043395996,0.0050582886,0.02192688,-0.018203735,-0.010307312,-0.011459351,-0.031799316,-0.0048599243,-0.01285553,-0.0009918213,0.0103302,-0.01751709,-0.0060691833,0.02983093