(2240,	NULL,	NULL,	'Permitir que dependencias institucionales, como la Dirección de Transformación Social, Gestión Humana, la Dirección de Aprendizaje y Asuntos Profesorales, Dirección de Educación Continua y Consultoría, Dirección de Éxito Estudiantil, Dirección de Investigación, Creación e Innovación o la Dirección de Programas Académicos, puedan solicitar formación específica para estudiantes, profesores o administrativos.
Características de esta oferta:
Flexible y adaptativa: Los cursos se diseñan por solicitud directa, según la demanda de cada unidad académica o administrativa.
Enfocados en habilidades aplicadas: Pueden cubrir herramientas como habilidades a solución de problemas mediante hojas de cálculo, herramientas informáticas, internet, y en general temas disciplinares específicos.
Modalidad variada: Dependiendo del perfil de los participantes, se puede ofrecer en modalidad presencial, teleclase, virtual o mixta.
Duración corta e intensiva: Cursos tipo bootcamp, talleres o microcredenciales.',	'[-0.039367676,0.025283813,0.07965088,0.01600647,-0.016479492,-0.020706177,0.008369446,0.074645996,0.015571594,0.031555176,0.02381897,-0.008605957,-0.0008330345,-0.028793335,-0.023620605,0.040740967,-0.0065574646,0.0024147034,0.0062294006,0.061462402,0.03881836,-0.021621704,-0.027130127,0.014060974,-0.0072669983,-0.00013661385,-0.009178162,0.03552246,-0.013687134,-0.01322937,0.0418396,-0.024841309,-0.08081055,0.0013198853,0.005508423,0.054779053,-0.018112183,0.07330322,0.033355713,-0.023757935,0.012756348,0.0090789795,-0.010597229,-0.009376526,-0.040039062,-0.016311646,-0.025527954,-0.0138168335,0.0055885315,0.056427002,-0.0501709,0.002817154,0.04763794,0.057647705,-0.02142334,0.000667572,-0.01626587,-0.012557983,-0.02015686,-0.020889282,0.059387207,-0.011474609,0.02973938,0.06225586,0.016342163,0.050598145,-0.050720215,-0.009292603,-0.0647583,0.018447876,0.028274536,-0.0049858093,-0.007408142,-0.016784668,0.0058135986,0.06402588,0.026290894,0.025894165,-0.02659607,0.017303467,0.023788452,-0.009544373,0.018539429,-0.017211914,-0.02255249,0.015548706,-0.050354004,-0.01309967,-0.017150879,-0.03161621,-0.036621094,0.011795044,-0.06549072,0.04425049,0.0010633469,0.03729248,-0.014442444,-0.046905518,0.02015686,0.062805176,0.060699463,-0.030838013,0.013259888,-0.025558472,0.003993988,-0.02154541,-0.018447876,-0.008216858,-0.027999878,0.010429382,0.029785156,-0.034942627,0.07110596,0.0022506714,0.02772522,-0.051452637,0.020523071,-0.03149414,-0.06518555,-0.0018873215,-0.008033752,-0.010093689,-0.023590088,-0.002090454,-0.024215698,-0.04598999,-0.0031356812,-0.011642456,-0.03439331,-0.056762695,-0.05340576,-0.01361084,0.00067949295,0.0032520294,-0.017303467,-0.024902344,-0.0340271,-0.017562866,-0.014190674,-0.06085205,0.045043945,-0.009292603,-0.0051879883,0.050445557,-0.05404663,-0.0049057007,0.0046691895,0.03704834,-0.0022602081,0.050445557,-0.018249512,-0.0028057098,-0.042297363,-0.02124023