(2241,	NULL,	NULL,	'Duración corta e intensiva: Cursos tipo bootcamp, talleres o microcredenciales.
Certificación institucional: Todos los cursos ofrecerán constancia de participación y en algunos casos insignias digitales si cumplen con una evaluación por competencia.
Punto de equilibrio: Los cursos tendrán un costo que debe cubrir los puntos de equilibrios definidos por el área financiera.
Esta oferta constituye un complemento estratégico a la ruta de competencias digitales, garantizando que la Universidad Autónoma de Bucaramanga esté preparada para formar a toda su comunidad universitaria, sin exclusión y con enfoque diferencial, en las herramientas necesarias para el aprendizaje, el trabajo y la transformación social desde lo digital.',	'[-0.025802612,0.025527954,0.053771973,0.013465881,-0.03353882,-0.009628296,0.035369873,0.059265137,0.030792236,0.007575989,0.028686523,-0.015213013,-0.010971069,-0.062042236,0.0071640015,0.07330322,-0.048461914,-0.0043907166,-0.0025520325,0.05886841,-0.00756073,-0.021896362,-0.009567261,0.025314331,0.025222778,-0.012458801,-0.013000488,0.034942627,-0.010543823,-0.019332886,0.035705566,-0.02746582,-0.05609131,-0.00969696,-0.0049209595,0.07861328,-0.005619049,0.07159424,0.059051514,-0.03567505,-0.016799927,-0.0124435425,-0.034820557,-0.05316162,-0.014442444,-0.035186768,0.008651733,0.006412506,-0.0033988953,0.066223145,-0.05529785,0.024673462,0.0647583,0.03677368,-0.03652954,-0.013458252,-0.03778076,-0.018600464,-0.013938904,0.007965088,0.045196533,-0.041381836,0.06173706,0.02746582,0.020874023,0.015792847,-0.054748535,0.0061454773,-0.047210693,-0.019744873,0.029205322,-0.013137817,0.00018298626,0.0059928894,0.011779785,0.05444336,0.018127441,-0.0132751465,0.011917114,-0.009643555,0.01953125,-0.012001038,0.051116943,-0.034484863,-0.011505127,0.02519226,-0.068237305,-0.021530151,-0.009010315,0.016921997,0.01146698,0.018081665,-0.034088135,0.031280518,-0.009963989,0.03277588,0.020736694,-0.028656006,0.013244629,0.045196533,0.022781372,-0.02029419,0.06060791,-0.068115234,0.011451721,-0.015151978,0.0113220215,-0.013710022,-0.015182495,0.0104904175,0.025497437,0.019882202,0.023788452,-0.007484436,0.042419434,-0.074157715,0.0013818741,-0.0395813,-0.026641846,-0.026504517,-0.006702423,-0.02432251,-0.028930664,-0.030761719,-0.036071777,-0.052093506,0.009788513,0.037475586,-0.02432251,-0.08190918,-0.007068634,-0.0017004013,0.0